quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaf. Pali Buku lolemekezeka la Korani
  50,2,"Koma iwo alikudabwa kuti kwa iwo kwadza mchenjezi wochokera pakati pawo. Motero anthu osakhulupirira amati, “chimenechi ndi chinthu chachilendo!”"
  50,3,"“Pamene ife tafa ndi kusanduka dothi, kubwerera kotero ndi kosatheka.”"
  50,4,Ife timadziwa onse amene adamezedwa ndi nthaka ndipo Ife tili ndi Buku la mbiri yawo
  50,5,"Iyayi, koma iwo adakana choonadi pamene chidadza kwa iwo. Kotero iwo, tsopano, asokonezeka"
  50,6,Kodi iwo sayang’ana kumwamba ndi kuona mmene tidakukonzera ndi kukukongoletsera ndi kuona kuti kulibe mipata
  50,7,Ndipo dziko lapansi Ife talipanga kukhala losalala ndi kuikamo mapiri ndipo tidameretsa mu dzikolo mbewu zokongola zosiyanasiyana
  50,8,Choonetsa ndi chikumbutso kwa kapolo aliyense amene amatembenukira nthawi zonse kwa Mulungu
  50,9,Ndipo timatumiza kuchokera ku mitambo mvula yodalitsika ndipo timameretsa m’minda mbewu zimene zimakololedwa
  50,10,Ndi mitengo italiitali ya tende yolemedwa ndi zipatso
  50,11,Chakudya cha akapolo. Ndipo Ife timapereka moyo kunthaka imene idali yakufa. Kumeneko ndiko kuuka kwa akufa
  50,12,"Adakana iwo asanadze, anthu a Nowa ndi iwo amene anali kukhala ku Ar-rass ndi Thamoud"
  50,13,Anthu a mtundu wa Aad ndi Farawo ndi abale ake a Loti
  50,14,"Ndi iwo amene anali kukhala m’nkhalango ndi anthu a ku Tuba, aliyense wa iwo adakana Atumwi ndipo chenjezo langa lidakwaniritsidwa"
  50,15,Kodi Ife tidatopa ndi chilengedwe choyamba? Iyayi. Iwo asokonezeka ndi nkhani zokhudza chilengedwe chatsopano
  50,16,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu ndipo timadziwa zimene mtima wake umamuuza. Ndipo Ife tili pafupi ndi iye kuposa mtsempha wa moyo wake
  50,17,"Pamene asungi awiri amulandira, wina atakhala kudzanja lamanja ndi wina ku dzanja lamanzere"
  50,18,Palibe mawu amene amayankhula amene samveka kwa Msungi wa tcheru
  50,19,Ndipo ululu wa imfa udzadza pa iye mwachoonadi. Ichi ndicho chimene iwe unali kuyesetsa kuchithawa
  50,20,Ndipo lipenga lidzaombedwa ndipo limeneli lidzakhala tsiku loopseza
  50,21,Ndipo mzimu uliwonse udzadza pamodzi ndi mngelo wouyendetsa ndi mngelo wochitira umboni
  50,22,"(Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa anthu ochimwa) kuti, “Ndithudi inu simudafune kuchenjezedwa za chimenechi ndipotsopano Ifetavundukulachimenechimakuphimbani. Ndipo lero maso anu ali kuona zenizeni.”"
  50,23,"Ndipo mnzake adzati, “Uwu ndi umboni umene ndili nawo.”"
  50,24,“Ponyani ku Gahena aliyense wosathokoza ndiponso wosamvera.”
  50,25,"“Woletsa kuchita ntchito zabwino, woswa malamulo ndiponso wokayika.”"
  50,26,"“Iye amene anali kukhazikitsa milungu ina yoonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, motero mponyeni ku chilango chowawa.”"
  50,27,"Mnzake adzanena kuti, “Ambuye wathu! Ine sindidamuuze kuti aziswa malamulo ayi koma iye adadzisocheretsa yekha.”"
  50,28,"Mulungu adzati, “Musakangane pamaso panga. Ine ndidakutumizirani chenjezo lokwanira.”"
  50,29,Chilango sichisintha ayi ndipo Ine sindionetsa chinyengo kwa akapolo anga
  50,30,"Patsiku limene Ife tidzaifunsa Gahena kuti, “Kodi mwadzadza?” Ndipo iyo idzati, “Kodi akanalipobe ena?”"
  50,31,Ndipo Paradiso idzabweretsedwa kufupi kwa anthu olungama
  50,32,Ichi ndicho chimene mudalonjezedwa ndipo ndi mphotho kwa iye amene amadzipereka kwa Mulungu nthawi zonse nasunga malamulo ake
  50,33,Ndiponso kwa iye amene amaopa Mwini chisoni chosatha wosaoneka ndipo amadza kwa Iye ndi mtima wodzichepetsa
  50,34,Lowani m’menemo mwamtendere ndi mosaopa ayi. Ili ndi tsiku la moyo wosatha
  50,35,M’menemo mudzakhala chilichonse chimene iwo adzafuna ndipo Ife tili ndi zinthu zambiri
  50,36,Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati imene Ife tidaiononga iwo asanabadwe amene adali ndi mphamvu zoposa iwo ndipo iwo adafuna chitetezo padziko? Kodi iwo anali ndi kwina kothawira
  50,37,Ndithudi muli chikumbutso mu zimenezi kwa iye amene ali ndi mtima kapena amatchera khutu pamene achenjezedwa
  50,38,Ndithudi Ife tidalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili m’menemo m’masiku asanu ndi limodzi ndipo sitidatope ayi
  50,39,Kotero pirira pa zonse zimene amanena ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako dzuwa lisanatuluke ndiponso lisanalowe
  50,40,Ndipo mulemekeze Iye usiku ndipo utatha kupemphera
  50,41,Ndipo udzamve patsiku limene woitana adzaitana kuchokera pafupi
  50,42,Tsiku limene iwo adzamva kulira kwa mfuwu woona. Limeneli lidzakhala tsiku louka kwa akufa
  50,43,Ndithudi ndife amene timapereka moyo ndi imfa ndipo ndi kwa Ife kumene zonse zidzabwerera
  50,44,Tsiku limene dziko lidzang’ambika ndipo iwo adzatuluka mofulumira. Kumeneko ndiko kudzakhala kusonkhanitsidwa pamodzi
  50,45,Ife timadziwa zonse zimene amanena ndipo iwe si ndiwe wankhanza ayi. Koma muchenjeze ndi Korani kwa aliyense amene aopa chilango changa
  51,1,Pali mphepo imene imamwaza fumbi
  51,2,Ndi mitambo imene ili yolemedwa ndi madzi
  51,3,Ndi zombo zimene zimayenda mosavutika ndi mwabata
  51,4,Ndipo pali iwo amene amagawa madalitso ndi chilolezo chathu
  51,5,"Ndithudi chimene mwalonjezedwa, ndithudi, ndi choona"
  51,6,Ndithudi chiweruzo chidzakwaniritsidwa
  51,7,Pali kumwamba kumene kuli njira zambiri
  51,8,Ndithudi inu muli ndi maganizo osiyana
  51,9,Amene abwezedwa ku icho ndiye amene wabwezedwa
  51,10,wotembereredwa akhale amene amanama
  51,11,Amene akutidwa ndi kusamvera
  51,12,"Iwo amafunsa kuti, “Kodi tsiku lachiweruzo lidzadza liti?”"
  51,13,"Tsiku limene iwo adzaweruzidwa ndi kuponyedwa ku Zariat\t559 moto"
  51,14,Lawani chilango chanu! Ichi ndicho chimene munali kufuna kuti chidze msanga
  51,15,Ndithudi iwo amene amalewa machimo adzakhala m’minda imene ili ndi a kasupe
  51,16,Kulandira zimene Ambuye wawo awapatsa. Ndithudi kale iwo anali kuchita zinthu zabwino
  51,17,Iwo anali kugona nthawi yochepa usiku
  51,18,Ndipo m’bandakucha anali kupempha chikhululukiro
  51,19,Ndipo mu chuma chawo mudali gawo limene linali kuperekedwa kwa anthu opempha ndi osowa
  51,20,Ndipo m’dziko muli zizindikiro kwa iwo okhulupirira
  51,21,Ndi mizimu yanu kodi simungaone
  51,22,Ndipo kumwamba ndiko kuli chakudya chanu ndi zimene muli kulonjezedwa
  51,23,"Ndiye, pali Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, chimenechi ndi cholinga ndi choonadi chomwe inu mumayankhula"
  51,24,Kodi udamva nkhani ya alendo olemekezeka a Abrahamu
  51,25,"Pamene iwo adadza kwa iye, iwo adati, “Mtendere.” Ndipo iye adati, “Mtendere.” Ndipo iye adati, “Inu ndinu alendo kwa ine.”"
  51,26,Ndipo iye atapita ku banja lake adabweretsa nyama ya ng’ombe yowotcha
  51,27,"Motero iye adadza nayo kwa iwo nati, “Kodi simufuna kudya?”"
  51,28,"Motero iye adayamba kuchita mantha mu mtima mwake. Ndipo iwo adati, “Usaope.” Ndipo iwo adamuuza nkhani yabwino yakubadwa kwa mwana wamwamuna yemwe adzakhala wanzeru kwambiri"
  51,29,"Ndipo mkazi wake adadza modzichepetsa ndipo adamenya pa mphumi pake nati, “Nkhalamba yaikazi yosaberekapo!”"
  51,30,"Iwo adati, “Ngakhale ndi choncho, Ambuye wako wayankhula. Iye ndi wodzala ndi luntha ndiponso nzeru.”"
  51,31,"Iye adati, “Kodi inu Atumwi uthenga wanu ndi wotani?”"
  51,32,"Iwo adati, “Ife tatumidwa kwa anthu ochimwa.”"
  51,33,“Kuti tigwetse pa iwo miyala yamakande.”
  51,34,“Idakonzedwa ndi Ambuye wako kudza kwa anthu oswa malamulo.”
  51,35,Ndipo Ife tidatulutsa anthu okhulupirira amene adali momwemo
  51,36,Koma sitidapezemo mabanja a Chisilamu kupatula banja limodzi lokha basi
  51,37,Ndipo Ife tidasiyamo chizindikiro kwa iwo amene amaopa chilango chowawa
  51,38,Ndi mwa Mose. Pamene tidamutumiza kwa Farawo ndi zizindikiro zooneka
  51,39,"Koma Farawo adakana pamodzi ndi mafumu ake nati, “Ndiwe munthu wamatsenga kapena munthu wa misala.”"
  51,40,Motero tidamugwira pamodzi ndi gulu la asirikali ake ndi kuwamiza onse m’nyanja pamene iye ndiye adali wolakwa
  51,41,Ndipo mwa a Aad pamene tidawatumizira mphepo yoononga
  51,42,Imene sidasiye chilichonse chimene idalimbana nacho kupatula kuchiononga ndi kuchisandutsa phulusa
  51,43,"Ndipo mwa anthu a Thamoud. Pamene adauzidwa kuti, “Basangalalani kanthawi kochepa.”"
  51,44,"Koma iwo adaphwanya lamulo la Ambuye wawo mwamwano, kotero mabingu adawaononga iwo ali kuona"
  51,45,Kotero iwo adalibe mphamvu zodzuka kapena zodzitetezera
  51,46,Ndi anthu a Nowa iwo asanadze. Ndithudi iwo adali anthu oswa malamulo
  51,47,"Ife tidakonza kumwamba mwamphamvu ndiponso mwaluso. Ndipo, ndithudi, ndife amene timapanga kukula kwa mlengalenga"
  51,48,"Ndipo dziko, tidamwaza. Kodi ndife omwaza bwino bwanji"
  51,49,Ndipo zonse zimene tidalenga tidazilenga ziwiriziwiri kuti mukhoza kukumbukira
  51,50,Kotero thawirani kwa Mulungu. Ndithudi Ine ndine mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,51,Ndipo musapange fano kukhala lopembedzedwa pamodzi ndi Mulungu. Ndithudi ine ndine mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,52,"Chimodzimodzi palibe Mtumwi amene adadza kwa anthu amene sadamunenere mawu ofanana monga akuti: “Wamatsenga kapena munthu wopenga!”"
  51,53,"Kodi uwu ndi mwambo umene akhala ali kusiyirana wina ndi mnzake? Iyayi, iwo ndi anthu amene ali kuswa malamulo mopyola muyeso"
  51,54,Kotero uwaleke chifukwa iwe ulibe mlandu
  51,55,Ndipo kumbutsa chifukwa chikumbutso chimathandiza anthu okhulupirira
  51,56,Ndipo Ine ndidalenga majini ndi anthu kuti azindipembedza Ine
  51,57,Ine sindiwapempha chakudya ndipo sindiwafunsa kuti azindidyetsa Ine
  51,58,"Ndithudi ndi Mulungu yekha amene amapereka chakudya chonse, Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi wolimba kwambiri"
  51,59,"Ndithudi anthu onse olakwa adzalandira gawo longa limene anzawo olakwa akale adalandira, kotero asandifunse Ine kuchita mofulumira"
  51,60,Kotero tsoka kwa onse osakhulupirira kuchokera ku tsiku lomwe iwo alonjezedwa
  52,1,Ndi pali phiri
  52,2,Ndi pali Buku lolemekezeka
  52,3,Lili chikopa chosapinda
  52,4,Ndi pali Bait – Ul-Ma’mur (Nyumba imene ili kumwamba yolingana ndi Kaaba imene ili ku Makka ndipo imaonedwa ndi angelo pafupipafupi)
  52,5,Ndi pali denga lonyamuka
  52,6,Ndi pali nyanja yodzadzidwa ndi madzi ambiri
  52,7,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako chidzakwaniritsidwa
  52,8,Palibe wina amene angachiletse
  52,9,"Pa tsiku limeneli, kumwamba kudzagwedezeka koopsa"
  52,10,Ndipo mapiri adzagudubuzika osakhalanso china chake
  52,11,"Kotero tsoka, patsiku limeneli kwa anthu abodza"
  52,12,Amene amatangwanika ndi mabodza
  52,13,Patsikuli iwo adzatengedwa ndi kuponyedwa mwamphamvu ku moto wa ku Gahena
  52,14,Uwu ndi moto umene mumati ndi bodza
  52,15,Kodi amenewa ndi matsenga kapena simutha kuona
  52,16,"Lawani kutentha kwake ndipo kaya inu mupirira kapena ayi, kwa inu ndi chimodzimodzi; inu muli kulandira malipiro a ntchito zomwe mumachita"
  52,17,"Ndithudi iwo amene ali olungama, adzakhala m’minda mwamtendere"
  52,18,Kusangalala chifukwa cha zimene Ambuye wawo wawapatsa ndipo Ambuye wawo wawapulumutsa ku chilango cha ku Gahena
  52,19,“Idyani ndi kumwa mwachisangalalo chifukwa cha ntchito zanu zabwino zomwe mudachita.”
  52,20,"Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo, yoikidwa m’mizere. Ndipo Ife tidzawakwatitsa kwa amene ali ndi maso akuluakulu ndi okongola"
  52,21,"Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira ndipo ana awo amawatsatira m’chipembedzo, oterewa tidzawakumaniza ndi mabanja awo ndipo Ife sitidzawachotsera chilichonse cha malipiro a ntchito zawo zabwino. Munthu aliyense adzafunsidwa malinga ndi ntchito zake"
  52,22,Ndipo tidzawapatsa zipatso ndi nyama zimene iwo afuna
  52,23,Kumeneko iwo adzapatsana wina ndi mnzake chikho chimene mulibe zinthu zopanda pake kapena uchimo
  52,24,Iwo adzazunguliridwa ndi kutchingidwa bwino ndi anyamata awoawo amene adzawatumizira ngati kuti iwo anali ndolo zobisika
  52,25,Ndipo iwo adzafunsana wina ndi mnzake ndi kuyankhulitsana
  52,26,"Iwo adzati, “Kale ife tidali a mantha ndi mabanja athu.”"
  52,27,“Koma Mulungu wationetsera chisomo chake ndipo watipulumutsa ife ku chilango cha kumoto.”
  52,28,“Ndithudi ife tinali kumupempha Iye yekha. Ndithudi Iye ndiye Mwini chifundo ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha.”
  52,29,"Motero pitiriza kukumbutsa ndi kulalikira. Chifukwa cha chisomo cha Ambuye wako, iwe si ndiwe munthu wonyenga kapena wamisala"
  52,30,"Kapena iwo amati, “Ndi Mlakatuli, ife tili kuyembekezera kuti choipa chidze pa iye.”"
  52,31,"Nena, “Yembekezerani! Nanenso ndili mmodzi wa oyembekezera.”"
  52,32,Kodi ndi maganizo awo amene ali kumawauza izi kapena iwo ndi anthu amene amaswa malamulo mosadodoma
  52,33,"Kodi kapena iwo amati, “Iye wapeka yekha uthengawu? Iyayi! iwo alibe chikhulupiriro.”"
  52,34,Alekeni nawo abweretse mawu olingana ndi awa ngati iwo ali kunena zoona
  52,35,Kodi iwo adalengedwa popanda china chake kapena iwo ndiwo a Namalenga
  52,36,Kapena ndiwo amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi? Iyayi! iwo alibe chikhulupiriro chokhazikika
  52,37,Kodi ndiwo amene amasunga chuma cha Ambuye wako? Kapena iwo ndiwo a nkhanza amene ali ndi ulamuliro wonena chilichonse chimene afuna
  52,38,Kodi kapena iwo ali ndi njira yomvetsera zomwe zinali kunenedwa? Motero mulekeni kazitape wawo kuti apereke umboni wokwanira
  52,39,Kodi kapena Iye ali ndi ana aakazi okha pamene inuyo muli ndi ana aamuna
  52,40,Kodi kapena iwe uli kuwafunsa malipiro kotero kuti iwo apanikizidwa kwambiri ndi ngongole
  52,41,Kodi kapena ali ndi zobisika ndipo amazilemba
  52,42,Kodi kapena ali kukonza chiwembu? Koma iwo amene sakhulupirira ndiwo amene ali ndi chiwembu
  52,43,Kodi kapena ali ndi mulungu wina kupatula Mulungu weniweni? Mulungu alemekezeke kuposa zimene iwo amamufanizira nazo
  52,44,"Ndipo iwo akadaona gawo lina la kumwamba lili kugwa pansi ndipo iwo akadati, “Ndi mitambo youndana.”"
  52,45,Motero alekeni mpaka pamene iwo akumana ndi tsiku lawo limene iwo adzakomoka ndi mantha
  52,46,Tsiku limene chiwembu sichidzawathandiza china chilichonse ndipo chithandizo sichidzaperekedwa kwa iwo
  52,47,"Ndipo, ndithudi, onse amene amachita zoipa, kuli chilango china pa chilango ichi koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa"
  52,48,"Motero pirira podikira chiweruzo cha Ambuye wako, chifukwa ndithudi iwe uli kusamalidwa ndi Ife ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako pamene uuka ku tulo"
  52,49,"Nthawi ya usiku, lemekeza ulemerero wake ndi pa nthawi yolowa nyenyezi"
  53,1,Ndi pali nyenyezi pamene ili kulowa
  53,2,M’bale wanu sadasochere kapena kuti ndi wolakwa
  53,3,Ndipo iye sayankhula zofuna zake
  53,4,Icho ndi chochita kuuzidwa kwa iye
  53,5,Iye adaphunzitsidwa ndi Iye amene ali ndi mphamvu
  53,6,"Wopanda chilema chilichonse, kotero adadzuka ndi kukhala wokhazikika"
  53,7,Pamene iye anali patali kwambiri mu mlengalenga
  53,8,Ndipo adasendera ndi kudza pafupi
  53,9,Ndipo adali pa mtunda wolingana kuponya mipaliro iwiri kapena kucheperapo
  53,10,Motero Iye adaulula Uthenga kwa kapolo wake kudzera mwa Gabriyele
  53,11,Mtima wake wa Mtumwi siudaname ponena zimene iye adaona
  53,12,Kodi inu mudzatsutsana naye pa zimene iye adaona
  53,13,Ndithudi iye adamuona iye pamene anali kutsika kachiwiri
  53,14,Pafupi ndi mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,15,Pafupi pake pali munda womwe ndi malo opumirako
  53,16,Ndipo chimene chimaphimba chidakuta mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,17,Maso ake sadayang’ane kumbali kapena kupyola muyeso
  53,18,Ndithudi iye adaona zizindikiro zazikulu kwambiri za Ambuye wake
  53,19,Kodi inu maganiza za Lat ndi Uzza
  53,20,Ndi Manat wachitatu wamkazi
  53,21,Kwa inu amuna ndipo kwa Iye akazi
  53,22,Ndithudi kumeneku ndiko kugawa kosalungama
  53,23,"Awa ndi mayina chabe amene inu mwapeka, inu ndi atate anu, amene Mulungu sadakulamuleni ndi pang’ono pomwe. Iwo amangotsatira nkhani zakumva chabe zimene mitima yawo imafuna pamene, ndithudi, kwadza kale kwa iwo ulangizi wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo"
  53,24,Kodi munthu angapeze zonse zimene amafuna
  53,25,Koma Mulungu ndiye Mwini moyo umene uli nkudza ndi moyo wakale
  53,26,Ndipo kuli angelo ambiri amene ali kumwamba amene kukhala pakati kwawo sikudzathandiza chilichonse kupatula pokhapo pamene Mulungu apereka chilolezo kwa amene Iye wamufuna ndi kukondweretsedwa naye
  53,27,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupirira za m’moyo umene uli nkudza, amatcha angelo ndi mayina achikazi"
  53,28,"Pamene iwo sadziwa chilichonse cha izo. Iwo satsatira china chilichonse koma nkhani zabodza ndipo, ndithudi, nkhani zabodza si mlowam’malo wa choonadi"
  53,29,Motero mupewe wina aliyense amene salabadira chikumbutso chathu ndipo safuna china chilichonse koma moyo wa padziko lino lapansi
  53,30,Uko ndiko kuchuluka kwa nzeru zawo. Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye amadziwa bwino onse amene amasochera ku njira yoyenera ndipo amadziwa kwambiri iye amene amatsata njira yoyenera
  53,31,"Ndipo Mulungu ndiye mwini wake wa chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, ndipo akhoza kulanga onse amene amachita zoipa molingana ndi ntchito zawo ndiponso kuti akhoza kulipira onse amene amachita zabwino ndi mphotho yabwino kwambiri"
  53,32,"Iwo amene amapewa machimo a akuluakulu ndi chigololo kupatula machimo a ang’onoang’ono, ndithudi, Ambuye wako ndi Mwini chikhululukiro. Iye amakudziwani bwino pamene amakulengani kuchokera ku dothi ndi pamene mukutidwa m’mimba mwa amayi anu. Motero musadziyeretse nokha. Al Najm\t567 Iye amadziwa bwino kwambiri aliyense amene amalewa zoipa"
  53,33,Kodi iwe wamuona amene amabwerera m’mbuyo
  53,34,Amene adapereka pang’ono ndipo anasiya kupereka
  53,35,Kodi iye amadziwa za zinthu zobisika kuti akhoza kuziona
  53,36,Kodi kapena iye sadauzidwe za mawu amene ali m’mabuku a Mose
  53,37,Ndiponso za Abrahamu amene adakwaniritsa malamulo
  53,38,Kuti palibe munthu amene adzasenza katundu wa mnzake
  53,39,Ndipo kuti munthu sadzapeza chilichonse kupatula chimene wachigwirira ntchito
  53,40,Ndipo kuti ntchito zake zidzaoneka
  53,41,Pamenepo iye adzalipidwa malipiro ake oyenera
  53,42,Ndipo kuti kwa Ambuye wanu ndi kumene nonse mudzapita
  53,43,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amawachititsa anthu kuseka ndi kuwaliritsa
  53,44,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"Ndiponso kuti Iye adalenga zinthu ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi"
  53,46,Kuchokera ku madontho a umuna umene umatuluka
  53,47,Ndipo kuti kwa Iye kuli chilengedwe chachiwiri
  53,48,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka chuma ndi chisangalalo
  53,49,Ndipo kuti Iye ndiye Ambuye wa nyenyezi yamphamvu yotchedwa Sirius
  53,50,Kuti ndiye amene adaononga anthu akale a mphamvu kwambiri a mtundu wa a Aad kale
  53,51,Ndi anthu a mtundu wa a Thamoud. Ndipo Iye sadasiye wina aliyense
  53,52,Ndi anthu a Nowa amakedzana ndithudi iwo adali osalungama ndi oswa malamulo mwamwano
  53,53,Ndipo iye adaononga mizinda yomwe idali yogonjetsedwa
  53,54,Kotero iwo adawavundikira nd chimene chidawavundikira
  53,55,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wako zimene udzazikayikira
  53,56,Uyu ndi mchenjezi wotsatizana ndi achenjezi a makedzana
  53,57,Tsiku louka kwa akufa lili pafupi
  53,58,Palibe wina kupatula Mulungu amene akhoza kulipherera
  53,59,Kodi inu mulikudabwa pa zimene zili kulakatulidwa
  53,60,Ndipo inu muli kuseka m’malo mwakulira
  53,61,Ndi kumapitirizabe kuchita zinthu zopanda pake
  53,62,Motero gunditsani nkhope zanu pansi ndipo pembedzani Mulungu mmodzi yekha
  54,1,Ola lachiweruzo lili pafupi ndipo mwezi wagawanika pakati
  54,2,"Koma iwo akaona chozizwitsa, sakhulupirira ndipo amati, “Ichi sichina ayi koma matsenga ozama.”"
  54,3,Iwo amakana choonadi koma amatsatira zilakolako zawo. Koma chinthu chilichonse chili ndi kumaliza kwake
  54,4,Ndithudi uthenga waperekedwa kale kwa iwo umene uli ndi chenjezo
  54,5,Wodzadzidwa ndi nzeru koma machenjezo ake sawathandiza iwo china chilichonse
  54,6,"Kotero iwe, asiye okha. Patsiku limene woitana adzawaitana kudza ku chinthu choopsa"
  54,7,"Iwo adzadza kumeneko ndi nkhope zogwa pansi, kuchokera kumanda awo monga dzombe louluka ponseponse"
  54,8,"Adzadza mofulumira kwa oitana anthu osakhulupirira adzati, “Ili ndi tsiku lovuta kwambiri.”"
  54,9,"Asanadze iwo, anthu a Nowa adakana kapolo wathu ndipo adati, “Uyu ndi munthu wamisala.” Ndipo iwo adamuthamangitsa iye ndi kumunyoza kwambiri"
  54,10,"Ndipo iye adadandaula kwa Ambuye wake nati, “Ndagonjetsedwa kotero idzani kuti mundithandize.”"
  54,11,"Motero Ife tidatsekula makomo a kumwamba, ndipo mvula idagwa nthawi yomweyo"
  54,12,Ndipo tidatumphutsa a kasupe padziko lapansi kotero madzi onse adakumana monga mwa lamulo lathu
  54,13,Ndipo tidamunyamula iye m’chombo chopangidwandimatabwandichokhomedwandimisomali
  54,14,Chidanyamuka potsogozedwa ndi Ife. Mphotho kwa iye amene adakanidwa
  54,15,Ndithudi tidachisiya icho ngati chizindikiro koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,16,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zalikulu bwanji
  54,17,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulidziwa ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,18,Anthu a Aad adakana. Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,19,Ndithudi Ife tidatumiza mphepo yamkhuntho pa tsiku latsoka losasimbika
  54,20,Kugwetsa anthu ngati kuti adali mathunthu a mitengo ya mgwalangwa yozulidwa
  54,21,Kodi chilango changa ndipo chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,22,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,23,Anthu a Thamoud adakana machenjezo
  54,24,"Iwo adati, “Munthu! Mmodzi yekha wochokera ku mtundu wathu kuti timutsatire? Ndithudi ife tikhala olakwa kwambiri ndiponso a misala.”"
  54,25,“Kodi ndiye kuti uthenga waperekedwa kwa iye yekha pakati pa ife tonse? Iyayi! Iye ndi wabodza ndi wodzikweza.”
  54,26,Mawa iwo adzadziwa kuti wabodza ndi wodzikweza ndani
  54,27,Ndithudi Ife titumiza ngamira yaikazi ngati mayesero kwa iwo. Motero iwe uwapenyetsetse ndipo ukhale wopirira
  54,28,Ndipo uwauze kuti azigawana madzi. Ndipo nthawi yomwera madzi idzakhazikitsidwa
  54,29,Ndipo iwo adaitana m’bale wawo ndipo iye adatulutsa lupanga ndi kuipha
  54,30,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,31,Ndithudi tidawatumizira mfuwu umodzi ndipo onse adali ngati nkhuni zodula zimene munthu womanga mpanda amatola
  54,32,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,33,Anthu a Loti adati chenjezo lathu ndi labodza
  54,34,Ndithudi Ife tidawatumizira mphepo yonyamula miyala kupatula a pa banja la Loti amene tidawapulumutsa mu ola lomaliza la usiku
  54,35,"Monga chisomo chochokera kwa Ife, motero ndi mmene timalipirira anthu oyamika"
  54,36,Ndithudi iye adawachenjeza za chilango chathu choopsa koma iwo adakana chenjezo lathu
  54,37,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo adafuna kuchititsa manyazi alendo ake. Motero Ife tidawachititsa khungu. Kotero inu lawani chilango changa ndi machenjezo anga"
  54,38,Ndithudi chilango chowawa chidadza pa iwo nthawi yam’mawa
  54,39,Kotero inu lawani chilango changa ndi machenjezo anga
  54,40,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,41,"Ndipo, ndithudi, machenjezo adadza kwa anthu a Farawo"
  54,42,Iwo adati machenjezo athu onse ndi abodza motero tidawaononga ndi chilango champhamvu yochuluka
  54,43,Kodi anthu anu osakhulupirira ndi abwino kuposa awa? Kapena inu muli ndi chitetezo mu m’mawu a Mulungu
  54,44,"Kodi kapena iwo amati, “Ife ndife ambiri ndipo tidzapambana?”"
  54,45,Tsopano magulu awo ali kupirikitsidwa ndipo iwo ali kuthawa
  54,46,"Iyayi, koma ola lachiweruzo ndi nthawi imene iwo adalonjezedwa ndipo ola limeneli lidzakhala loopsa kwambiri"
  54,47,Ndithudi anthu osakhulupirira ndi olakwa adzapsya
  54,48,"Tsiku limene iwo adzaduduluzidwa pa nkhope zawo kunka ku moto, (zidzanenedwa) “Lawani ululu wa ku Moto.”"
  54,49,Ndithudi tidalenga chilichonse molingana ndi muyeso wake
  54,50,Ndipo ulamuliro wathu ndi umodzi monga kuphenira kwa diso
  54,51,Ndithudi Ife tidaononga kale anthu onga inu koma kodi alipo amene anga chenjezedwe
  54,52,Ndipo zonse zimene adachita zidalembedwa
  54,53,Ndipo chilichonse chaching’ono ndi chachikulu chidalembedwa kale
  54,54,Ndithudi onse amene amalewa zoipa adzakhala m’kati mwa minda ndi mitsinje
  54,55,Ku Paradiso kufupi ndi Mfumu yamphamvu zonse
  55,1,Mwini Chifundo Chosatha
  55,2,Ndiye amene adamphunzitsa munthu Korani
  55,3,Ndiye amene adalenga munthu
  55,4,Wamuphunzitsa iye mawu anzeru
  55,5,Dzuwa ndi mwezi zimayenda m’misewu imene zinalamulidwa
  55,6,Zomera (kapena nyenyezi) ndi mitengo zonse zimagwada pomulambira Iye
  55,7,Iye adakweza kumwamba ndi kukhazikitsa muyeso
  55,8,Kuti inu musaphwanye muyeso
  55,9,Kotero khazikitsani muyeso wachilungamo ndipo musayese monyenga
  55,10,Ndiye amene adalenga dziko lapansi kuti zolengedwa zake zizikhalamo
  55,11,Mu ilo muli zipatso ndi mitengo ya tende yobereka phava la zipatso zambiri
  55,12,Ndi chimanga chimene masamba ndi mapesi ake amadyedwa ndi ziweto. Ndi mitengo yonunkhira
  55,13,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,14,Iye adalenga munthu kuchokera ku dothi monga dothi la mbiya
  55,15,Ndipo adalenga majini kuchokera kumoto wopanda utsi
  55,16,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,17,Ambuye wa kum’mawa kuwiri ndi Ambuye wa kumadzulo kuwiri
  55,18,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,19,Iye adasiya nyanja ziwiri kuti zikumane
  55,20,Pakati pawo pali malire amene madzi a uku sangathe kudutsa kupita uko
  55,21,"Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Rahman\t573 Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana"
  55,22,Mu zonse muli nkhombe zazikulu ndi zazing’ono
  55,23,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,24,"Ndipo zake ndi zombo zimene zimayenda pa nyanja, zazikulu ngati mapiri"
  55,25,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,26,Zonse zimene zili pa dziko zidzatha
  55,27,Ndipo nkhope ya Ambuye wako mu Ufumu ndi mu Ulemerero idzakhalabe mpaka kalekale
  55,28,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,29,Zonse zimene zimakhala kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi zimapempha kwa Iye. Tsiku lililonse Iye amakhala ndi chochita
  55,30,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,31,"Ife tidzadza kwa inu, Oh inu magulu awiri"
  55,32,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,33,"oh inu gulu la Majini ndi Anthu! Ngati muli ndi mphamvu zodutsa malire a kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, dutsani. Komatu inu simungadutse popanda chilolezo"
  55,34,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,35,Malawi a moto ndi utsi zidzaponyedwa kwa inu nonse awiri ndipo simudzatha kudziteteza nokha
  55,36,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,37,Ndi pamene thambo lidzagawanika pakati ndikukhala lofiira ngati mafuta osungunuka
  55,38,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,39,"Motero patsiku limeneli, sipadzakhala mafunso kuchokera kwa Munthu kapena Majini okhudza machimo awo"
  55,40,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,41,ochimwa adzadziwika ndi zizindikiro ndipo adzawagwira tsumba ndi pamapazi pawo
  55,42,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye
  55,43,Iyi ndi Gahena imene anthu ochimwa amati ndi bodza
  55,44,Iwo adzalowa m’kati mwake ndi m’kati mwa madzi ogaduka
  55,45,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,46,"Ndipo kwa iye amene aopa kuima pamaso pa Ambuye wawo, kudzakhala minda iwiri"
  55,47,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,48,Zokhala ndi mphanda zotambasuka
  55,49,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti zaAmbuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,50,Monse mudzakhala a kasupe awiri otumphuka
  55,51,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,52,M’menemu mudzakhala zipatso ziwiriziwiri za mitundumitundu
  55,53,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,54,Iwo adzagona pa makama amene nsalu yake ya m’kati idzakhala yasilika ndipo zipatso za m’minda iwiriyi zidzakhala pafupi pawo
  55,55,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,56,M’menemo mudzakhala wodzisunga ndi ogwetsa nkhope zawo pansi amene Munthu kapena Majini sadawakhudze
  55,57,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,58,olingana ndi miyala ya rubiya ndi ndolo
  55,59,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,60,Kodi dipo la ntchito yabwino lingakhale lina loposa ubwino
  55,61,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,62,Ndipo poonjezera pa minda iwiri pali minda ina iwiri
  55,63,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,64,Yooneka mobiriwira
  55,65,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,66,Monse mudzakhala a kasupe awiri otulutsa madzi ochuluka
  55,67,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,68,"Monse mudzakhala zipatso, tende ndi chimanga chachizungu"
  55,69,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,70,Mmenemo mudzakhala zinthu zokongola
  55,71,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,72,Angwiro ndi okhala m’mahema
  55,73,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,74,Amene Munthu kapena Majini sadawakhudze
  55,75,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,76,"Atakhala pa mipando yawofowofo, yobiriwira ndi mabedi okongola"
  55,77,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,78,"Lidalitsike dzina la Ambuye wako, Mwini ulemerero, chuma ndi ulemu"
  56,1,Pamene ola la chiweruzo lidza
  56,2,Ndipo palibe mzimu umene udzakana kudza kwake
  56,3,Kutsitsa gulu lina ndikukweza gulu linzake
  56,4,Pamene dziko lidzagwedezeka ndi chigwedezo choopsya
  56,5,Ndi pamene mapiri adzafumbutuka kukhala fumbi lokhalokha
  56,6,Motero iwo adzakhala fumbi louluzika paliponse
  56,7,Ndipo inu mudzagawidwa m’magulu atatu
  56,8,Iwo a ku dzanja la manja. Kodi a ku dzanja la manja adzakhala ndani
  56,9,Iwo akudzanja la mazere. Kodi akudzanja la mazere adzakhala ndani
  56,10,Ndipo gulu la iwo amene adzakhala kutsogolo m’chikhulupiriro adzakhala kutsogolo m’moyo umene uli nkudza
  56,11,Awa ndiwo amene adzakhala kufupi ndi Mulungu
  56,12,M’minda ya Paradiso
  56,13,Gulu lalikulu lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya kale
  56,14,Ndi gulu lochepa lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya m’mbuyo mwake
  56,15,Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo yomatidwa golide ndi miyala ya mtengo wapatali
  56,16,Atakhala pa iyo ndi kumayang’anizana
  56,17,Iwo adzatumikiridwa ndi anyamata a muyaya
  56,18,"Ndi mabakuli, miphika ndi zikho za vinyo wabwino"
  56,19,Amene sadzawawitsa mitu yawo kapena kuwatopetsa
  56,20,Ndi zipatso zimene adzasankhepo
  56,21,Ndi nyama ya nkhuku imene angafune
  56,22,"Ndipo padzakhala anzawo okongola, a maso akulu ndi ochititsa kaso"
  56,23,Monga ndolo zosamalidwa bwino
  56,24,Malipiro a ntchito zimene adachita kale
  56,25,Palibe nkhani zopanda pake kapena zolaula zimene adzamva
  56,26,"Kupatula mawu akuti Mtendere, Mtendere"
  56,27,"Iwo a kudzanja lamanja, kodi akudzanja lamanja adzakhala ndani"
  56,28,Iwo adzakhala pakati pa m’mithunzi ya mitengo ya Sidrah
  56,29,Ndi m’mapata a nthochi zokhala ndi mikoko wina pamwamba pa unzake
  56,30,M’mithunzi yotambasuka
  56,31,Pambali pa madzi osefukira
  56,32,Ndi zipatso zochuluka
  56,33,Zimene nyengo yake sikutha ndipo kuchuluka kwake kudzakhalabe
  56,34,Ndi pa mipando yawofowofo yokwezedwa
  56,35,Ndithudi Ife tawalenga iwo mu chilengedwe cha padera
  56,36,Ndi kuwapanga kukhala a Namwali abwino
  56,37,A chikondi pa anzawo olingana nawo zaka
  56,38,A iwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja
  56,39,"Gulu lochuluka lidzakhala lochokera ku mibadwo yoyamba, yakale"
  56,40,Gulu lochuluka lidzakhala lochokera ku mibadwo ya pambuyo pake
  56,41,Gulu la anthu a kudzanja lamanzere. Kodi anthu a kudzanja la manzere adzakhala otani
  56,42,M’katikati mwa malawi a moto ndi m’madzi ogaduka
  56,43,Ndi m’mithunzi ya utsi wakuda
  56,44,Yosazizira kapena yabwino
  56,45,Ndithudi iwo kale adali kukhala m’moyo wosavutika ndi opeza zinthu zambiri
  56,46,Ndipo adapitirira kuchita zoipa zikulu zikulu
  56,47,"Ndipo iwo anali kukonda kunena kuti: “Pamene ife tafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, kodi tingadzaukitsidwenso?”"
  56,48,“Ndi makolo athu a nthawi ya makedzana?”
  56,49,"Nena: “Ndithudi onse oyambirira ndi otsiriza.”"
  56,50,“Ndithudi onse adzasonkhanitsidwa pamodzi pa tsiku lokhazikitsidwa.”
  56,51,“Kuphatikiza inu nonse amene muchimwa ndi kukana choonadi.”
  56,52,“Ndithudi inu mudzadya zipatso za mtengo wa Zaqqoom.”
  56,53,“Ndipo mudzakhutitsa mimba zanu ndi izo.”
  56,54,“Ndi kumwa madzi ogaduka.”
  56,55,“Ndi kumwa monga momwe ngamira yodwala ndi yaludzu imamwera.”
  56,56,Kumeneko ndiko kudzakhala kusangalala kwawo patsiku lachiweruzo
  56,57,Ndife amene tidakulengani inu nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simukhulupilira
  56,58,Ndiuzeni za umuna umene mumatulutsa
  56,59,Kodi ndinu amene mumaulenga kapena Ife ndife timaulenga
  56,60,Ife tidalamulira imfa kukhala pakati panu ndipo Ife sitingagonjetsedwe ayi
  56,61,Kukusinthani inu ndi kukulengani kukhala china chake chimene inu simuchidziwa
  56,62,Ndithudi inu mumadziwa za chilengedwe choyamba. Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simulabadira
  56,63,Kodi mudayamba mwaganiza za mbewu imene mumabzala
  56,64,Kodi ndinu amene mumaimeretsa kapena ndife amene timameretsa
  56,65,"Ngati titafuna, Ife tikadaiphwanya m’timagawomagawo touma ndipo inu mukadayamba kudandaula"
  56,66,Ndithudi ife tapatsidwa chingongole cholemera
  56,67,Iyayi. Koma tamanidwa
  56,68,Kodi inu mumawaona madzi amene mumamwa
  56,69,Kodi ndinu amene mumawagwetsa kuchokera ku mitambo kapena ndife
  56,70,Chikadakhala chifuniro chathu tikadawapanga iwo kukhala a mchere. Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simuthokoza
  56,71,Kodi inu mumaganizira za moto umene mumasonkha
  56,72,Kodi ndinu amene mumameretsa mtengo umene umayaka moto kapena ndife amene timaumeretsa
  56,73,Ife taupanga iwo kukhala chikumbutso ndi chinthu chothandiza anthu amene ali paulendo
  56,74,Kotero lemekezani dzina la Ambuye wanu Wamkulu
  56,75,Ndipo ndilumbira pali nyenyezi zimene zili kugwa
  56,76,Ndithudi ili ndi lonjezo lalikulu inu mukadadziwa
  56,77,Ndithudi ndi Buku lolemekezeka la Korani
  56,78,Limene lili m’Buku lotetezedwa
  56,79,Palibe amene adzalikhudza kupatula oyeretsedwa okha
  56,80,Chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  56,81,Kodi muli kunyozabe uthenga uwu
  56,82,Mmalo mothokoza chifukwa cha zinthu zimene amakupatsani inu mumamukana Iye
  56,83,Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani inu simuthandiza pamene mzimu wa munthu amene ali kufa ufika pa khosi pake
  56,84,"Pamene panthawiyo, inu mumangoyang’ana"
  56,85,Koma Ife tili pafupi ndi iye kuposa inu koma inu simutiona
  56,86,Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simutero ngati inu simudzaweruzidwa patsogolo pake
  56,87,Bwezerani mzimuwo ngati ndinu anthu a choonadi
  56,88,Ndipo ngati iye ndi mmodzi wa anthu amene ali kufupi ndi Mulungu
  56,89,Iye adzapeza mpumulo ndi chakudya ndi munda wa chisangalalo
  56,90,Ndipo ngati iye ndi wam’gulu la anthu akudzanja la manja
  56,91,Kotero kuli mtendere kwa iwo a kudzanja lamanja
  56,92,Ndipo ngati iye ndi mmodzi wa iwo okana choonadi ndi amene amalakwa
  56,93,Motero kulandiridwa kwake kudzakhala kwa madzi otentha kwambiri
  56,94,Ndi kulowetsedwa ku Gahena
  56,95,Ndithudi ichi ndi choonadi chosakayikitsa
  56,96,"Motero lemekezani dzina la Ambuye wanu, Wamkulu"
  57,1,"Chilichonse chimwe chili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi chimalemekeza Mulungu. Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu, Mwini nzeru"
  57,2,Wake ndi Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi. Ndiye amene amapereka moyo ndi imfa ndipo ali ndi mphamvu pa zinthu zonse
  57,3,"Iye ndi woyamba ndi womaliza, wapamwamba mwamba ndi wapafupi. Ndipo Iye amadziwa zinthu zonse"
  57,4,"Ndiye adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi m’masiku asanu ndi limodzi ndipo adabuka pa mwamba pa mpando wake wa Chifumu. Iye amadziwa chilichonse chimene chimalowa m’nthaka ndi chilichonse chimene chimatuluka mu iyo, zonse zimene zimadza pansi kuchokera kumwamba ndi zonse zimene zimakwera kumwamba. Ndipo Iye ali nanu kulikonse kumene mungakhale. Ndipo Mulungu amaona zonse zimene mumachita"
  57,5,Wake ndi Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi. Ndipo ndi kwa Iye kumene zonse zimabwerera
  57,6,Iye amapanga usiku kulumikizana ndi usana ndi kupanga usana kulumikizana ndi usiku. Iye amadziwa zinsinsi zonse zili m’mitima
  57,7,"Khulupirirani mwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Perekani zopereka zaulere kuchokera ku zinthu zimene Mulungu wakupatsani kuti zikhale zanu. Iwo a inu amene akhulupilira ndipo apereka chaulere, yawo idzakhala mphotho yaikulu"
  57,8,"Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani kuti inu simukhulupirira mwa Mulungu? Pamene Mtumwi ali kukuitanani kuti mukhulupirire mwa Ambuye wanu ndipo Iye, ndithudi, walandira lonjezo lanu ngati inu ndinu anthu okhulupirira"
  57,9,"Ndiye amene amatumiza kwa kapolo wake zizindikiro zooneka kuti akhoza kukutsogolerani inu kuchoka ku mdima waukulu kupita kowala. Ndipo, ndithudi, Mulungu, kwa inuyo, ndi wachifundo ndi wachisoni"
  57,10,"Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani inu simufuna kupereka m’njira ya Mulungu? Mulungu ndiye Mwini wa zonse zili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi. Palibe ofanana, pakati panu, ndi iwo amene amapereka chaulere ndipo adamenya nawo nkhondo poyamba kupambana kusanadze. Amenewa ndi a pamwamba kuposa iwo amene adapereka chaulere ndi kumenya nkhondo pambuyo pake. Koma kwa onsewa, Mulungu walonjeza mphotho yokoma. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene mumachita"
  57,11,Kodi ndani amene adzakongoza Mulungu ngongole yabwino kuti Iye aipindulitse ndipo kuti iye adzakhale ndi mphotho ina yapamwamba
  57,12,"Patsiku limeneli inu mudzaona amuna okhulupirira ndi akazi okhulupirira, nyali zawo zili kuyaka patsogolo pawo ndi kudzanja lawo lamanja, kulonjerana kwawo kudzakhala nkhani yabwino kwa inu lero lino! Minda imene pansi pake pamayenda madzi mudzakhala m’menemo mpaka kalekale. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwenikweni"
  57,13,"Patsiku limene amuna a chinyengo ndi akazi a chinyengo adzanena kwa iwo okhulupirira:“Tidikirirenikutitikhozakulandirachilangali kuchokera ku muuni wanu.” Koma kudzanenedwa kuti: “Bwererani m’mbuyo kuti mukafune muuni wanu. Ndipo chipupa chidzakhazikitsidwa pakati pawo chokhala ndi khomo. Mbali ina ya chipupachi kudzakhala chisomo pamene mbali ina kudzakhala chilango.”"
  57,14,"Iwo adzalira kwa iwo. “Kodi inu sitinali kukhalira limodzi?” Okhulupilira adzayankha kuti: “Zoonadi koma inu mudadzisocheretsa nokha. Inu mudanyengedwa, mudakayikira ndipo zilakolako zanu zidakunyengani inu mpaka pamene chilango cha Mulungu chinachitika. Ndipo wonyenga adakunyengani inu pa nkhani zokhudza Mulungu.”"
  57,15,"Motero lero palibe chiphuphu chimene chidzalandiridwa kuchokera kwa inu kapena iwo amene adakana Mulungu. Malo anu okhala ndi kumoto, amenewo ndiwo malo okhawo amene mudzalandiridwako ndipo ndi malo oipitsitsa kukhalamo"
  57,16,"Kodi nthawi siinakwane yoti okhulupirira enieni apereke mitima yawo modzichepetsa ndipo kuti azikumbukira Mulungu ndi choonadi chimene chavumbulutsidwa kwa iwo ndipo kuti asakhale ngati iwo amene adapatsidwa Buku nthawi ya kale? Koma patapita nthawi, mitima yawo idalimba. Ndipo ambiri a iwo ndi ophwanya malamulo"
  57,17,Dziwani kuti Mulungu amapereka moyo ku nthaka ikafa. Ndithudi taonetsa chivumbulutso chathu poyera kwa inu kuti mukhoza kuzindikira
  57,18,"Ndithudi iwo amene amapereka chopereka chaulere, amuna kapena akazi, iwo amasunga gawo lawo kwa Mulungu lomwe lidzaonjezeredwa mopitiriza muyeso ndipo adzakhala ndi mphotho yolemekezeka"
  57,19,"Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi mwa Mtumwi wake, iwo ndi olungama ndi okhulupirira pamaso pa Ambuye wawo. Iwo adzalandira mphotho yawo pamodzi ndi muuni. Ndipo iwo amene sakhulupirira ndipo amakana chivumbulutso chathu, amenewa ndiwo a ku moto wa ku Gahena"
  57,20,"Dziwani kuti moyo wa padziko lino lapansi ndi masewera ndi wotailako nthawi, chionetsero ndi kunyada ndi mpikisano pakati pa wina ndi mnzake wofuna chuma ndi ana. Fanizo lake lili ngati mvula ndi zomera zimene zimadza chifukwa cha zimene zimabweretsa chisangalalo kwa ozilima. Pasanapite nthawi izo zimafota ndi kuoneka za chikasu. Ndipo zimauma ndi kugwa pansi. Koma m’moyo umene uli kudza, kuli chilango chowawa kwa anthu ogona m’machimo ndi chikhululukiro chochokera kwa Mulungu ndiponso chisangalalo chake kwa iwo amene amadzipereka kwa Mulungu. Kodi moyo wa padziko lino lapansi ndi chiyani kupatula chinyengo chabe"
  57,21,Kotero fulumirani kupeza chikhululukiro cha Mulungu ndi munda wa Paradiso umene kutalika kwake kuli ngati kukula kwa kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi umene udakonzedwera iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi Atumwi ake. Chimenechi ndicho chisomo cha Mulungu chimene amapereka kwa amene Iye wamufuna. Mulungu ndi Ambuye wa chisomo chosatha
  57,22,Palibe vuto limene limadza padziko kapena pa inu limene silinakhazikitsidwe kale Ife tisanalibweretse. Ndithudi chimenechi ndi chosavuta kwa Mulungu
  57,23,Kuti inu musakhumudwe chifukwa cha zinthu zabwino zimene simudazipeze kapena kunyada chifukwa cha zokoma zimene zaperekedwa kwa inu. Mulungu sakonda anthu odzikundikira
  57,24,"Ndiponso anthu a umbombo amauza anzawo kuti nawonso azikhala a umbombo. Ngati wina abwerera m’mbuyo kuchokera ku njira ya Mulungu, ndithudi, Mulungu sasowa chilichonse ndipo ndi wolemekezeka"
  57,25,Ndithudi tidatumiza kale Atumwi athu ndi zizindikiro zooneka ndipo tidatumiza pamodzi ndi iwo Buku ndi muyeso kuti anthu akhoza kukhala ndi makhalidwe abwino. Ndipo Ife tidapanga chitsulo chimene m’kati mwake muli mphamvu ndi zinthu zambiri zabwino kwa anthu. Kuti Mulungu akhoza kuyesa iwo amene amamuthandiza Iye ndi Mtumwi wake mwamseri. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wolimba ndi wamphamvu
  57,26,Ndithudi Ife tidatumiza Nowa ndi Abrahamu ndipo tidapereka kwa ana awo mphatso ya Utumwi ndi Buku ndipo ena pakati pawo ndi otsogozedwa bwino koma ambiri ndi ophwanya malamulo
  57,27,"Ndipo tidawapanga Atumwi athu kuti atsatire m’mapazi mwawo; Ndipo tidatumiza Yesu, mwana wa Maria, pambuyo pake ndipo tidamupatsa Uthenga wabwino. Ndipo tidaika m’mitima mwa iwo amene adali kumutsatira iye kukoma mtima ndi chisoni. Ukakhala unsembe iwo adapeka okha, chifukwa Ife sitidawalamulire kuti akhazikitse kupatula kuti azifunafuna chisangalalo cha Mulungu koma iwo sadazilabadire ayi. Kotero tidawapatsa mphotho iwo amene adakhulupirira koma ambiri a iwo ndi oswa malamulo"
  57,28,oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Samalani udindo wanu kwa Mulungu ndipo mukhulupilire mwa Mtumwi wake. Iye adzakupatsani magawo awiri a chisomo chake ndikukonzerani muuni umene muzidzayenda nawo ndi kukukhululukirani machimo anu. Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wachisoni chosatha
  57,29,Kuti anthu a m’Buku adziwe kuti iwo alibe mphamvu ina iliyonse pa chisomo cha Mulungu ndipo kuti chisomo chake chili m’manja mwake mokha ndipo amachipereka kwa aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Mulungu ndiye Mwini mphatso zosatha
  58,1,Ndithudi Mulungu wamva mau a mkazi amene ali kutsutsana ndi iwe pa nkhani ya mwamuna wake ndipo iye wapereka madandaulo ake kwa Mulungu. Ndipo Mulungu wamva kukangana kwanu chifukwa Iye amamva ndiponso amaona chili chonse
  58,2,"Iwo amene ali pakati panu ndipo amasudzula akazi awo ponena kuti: “Iwe uli ngati msana wa Amai anga.” Iwo sangakhale Amai awo ai. Palibe amene angakhale amayi awo, kupatula okhawo amene anawabara. Ndithudi iwo amalankhula mau oipa ndi bodza. Ndithudi Mulungu amakhululukira nthawi zonse"
  58,3,Ndipo iwo amene amasudzula akazi ponena kuti amaoneka ngati kumbuyo kwa amayi awo kenaka afuna kuti akhululukidwe pa zomwe adanena ayenera kumasula kapolo asanabwererane. Limeneli ndi lamulo limene mwalamulidwa kuti mulimvere ndipo Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  58,4,"Ndipo ngati wina sangathe kutero, ayenera kusala chakudya miyezi iwiri mosadukiza asanabwererane. Koma ngati sangathe kutero, ayenera kudyetsa anthu osauka makumi asanu ndi limodzi; ndi cholinga chakuti muonetse chikhulupiriro mwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Amenewa ndiwo malamulo amene adakhazikitsidwa ndi Mulungu. Ndipo kwa anthu osakhulupilira kuli chilango chowawa"
  58,5,Ndithudi onse amene amatsutsa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wakeadzatsitsidwakwambirimongamomweadatsitsidwira iwo amene adalipo kale. Ndipo Ife tatumiza zizindikiro zooneka. Ndipo anthu onse osakhulupirira adzalandira chilango chochititsa manyazi
  58,6,Patsiku limene Mulungu adzawaukitsa onse kwa akufa ndi kuwauza ntchito zawo zonse zimene adachita. Mulungu anasunga zimene iwo adaiwala. Ndipo Mulungu ndi mboni pazinthu zonse
  58,7,"Kodi iwe siudaone kuti Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene zili mlengalenga ndi chilichonse chimene chili padziko lapansi? Palibe nkhani za chinsinsi pakati pa anthu atatu zimene Iye sakhala wachinayi, kapena pakati pa anthu asanu pamene Iye sakhala wa chisanu ndi chimodzi, kapena pakati pa anthu ochepa kapena ochuluka, koma Iye amakhala pakati pawo. Kulikonse kumene iwo angakhale pomaliza Iye adzawauza zonse zimene adachita patsiku lachiweruzo. Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse"
  58,8,"Kodi iwe siudawaone amene adaletsedwa kuchita misonkhano ya mseri komabe amayambanso kuchita misonkhano ya chinsinsi imene adaletsedwa kuti asamachite? Iwo amachita misonkhano pakati pawo ndi cholinga choukira ndi kusamvera Mtumwi wa Mulungu. Koma iwo akamadza kwa iwe, iwo amakulonjera iwe osati monga mmene Mulungu amakulonjerera ayi koma mwachinyengo. Ndipo iwo amati kwa wina ndi mnzake: “Kodi bwanji Mulungu satilanga pa zimene timanena?” Gahena ndi yokwana kwa iwo, ndipo adzapsa m’malawi ake. Ndipo kumeneko ndi konyansa kwambiri"
  58,9,"oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Pamene inu muchita misonkhano yanu yamseri musalankhule zinthu zoipa, zoukira ndi zosamvera Mtumwi koma muzilankhula zinthu zachilungamo ndi zamvano. Ndipo muopeni Mulungu chifukwa ndi kumene nonse mudzabwerera"
  58,10,Misonkhano yamseri imachokera kwa Satana amene amafuna kusokoneza anthu okhulupirira. Koma Iye sangawalakwitse ayi kupatula ndi chilolezo cha Mulungu ndipo mwa Mulungu ndi momwe anthu okhulupirira ayenera kuika chikhulupiriro chawo
  58,11,"Oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Ngati muuzidwa kukonza malo m’misonkhano yanu, konzani malo okwanira. Ndipo Mulungu adzakukonzerani inu malo okwanira kwambiri. Ndipo mukauzidwa kuti mudzuke, dzukani. Mulungu adzakweza mu maudindo ena a inu amene mukhulupirira ndi iwo amene apatsidwa nzeru. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa ntchito zanu zonse"
  58,12,"oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Ngati mufuna kukumana ndi Mtumwi mwamseri, perekani chaulere chanu musanayambe kukambirana naye. Zimenezo zidzakhala zabwino kwa inu ndiponso dongosolo. Koma ngati inu mulibe chopereka, Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi Mwini chisonichosatha"
  58,13,"Kodiinumulikuchitamanthakupereka chaulere chanu musanakumane naye? Ngati nditero, musachite mantha chifukwa Mulungu wakukhululukirani. Motero pitirizani kupemphera nthawi zonse, perekani msonkho wothandiza osauka, ndipo mverani Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa ntchito zanu zonse"
  58,14,"Kodi iwe suwaona amene amapalana ubwenzi ndi anthu amene adalandira mkwiyo wa Mulungu? Iwo si a m’gulu lako kapena a mgulu lawo, ndipo iwo amalumbira zabodza pamene ali kudziwa"
  58,15,Mulungu wawakonzera chilango chowawa. Ndithudi zoipa ndizo anali kuchita
  58,16,Iwo apanga malonjezo awo kukhala chishango. Kotero iwo amatchinjiriza anthu ku njira ya Mulungu ndipo iwo adzalandira chilango chochititsa manyazi
  58,17,Chuma kapena ana awo sizidzawathandiza ku mkwiyo wa Mulungu. Iwo adzapita kumoto kumene adzakhaleko mpaka kalekale
  58,18,"Patsiku limene Mulungu adzawadzutsa onse, iwo adzalumbira pamaso pake monga momwe alumbirira kwa inu. Ndipo iwo amaganiza kuti ali ndi mtsamiro. Ndithudi iwo ndi abodza"
  58,19,Satana ndiye ali kuwalamulira. Ndipo wawachititsa iwo kuti aiwale kukumbukira Mulungu. Iwo ali m’gulu la Satana. Ndithudi gulu la Satana lidzakhala lolephera
  58,20,Iwo amene amatsutsa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake adzakhala pakati pa anthu amene adzanyozedwa zedi
  58,21,"Mulungu walamulira kuti: Ndithudi! Ine pamodzi ndi Atumwi anga tidzapambana. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wamphamvu zonse"
  58,22,"Iwe sudzapeza anthu amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi tsiku lomaliza ali kuchita chibwenzi ndi iwo amene amatsutsa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake ngakhale kuti atakhala abambo wawo, kapena ana awo kapena abale awo kapena anansi awo. Kwa awa, Iye wakhazikitsa chikhulupiriro m’mitima mwawo, ndipo wawalimbikitsa ndi ulangizi, wochokera kwa Iye. Ndipo Iye adzawalandira m’minda ya Paradiso, imene pansi pake pamayenda mitsinje kuti akhale komweko mpaka kalekale. Mulungu wasangalala nawo ndipo nawonso asangalala ndi Iye. Iwo ndi anthu a gulu la Mulungu. Ndithudi ndi anthu a Mulungu amene adzapambana"
  59,1,Chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi chimalemekeza Mulungu. Ndipo Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi wanzeru
  59,2,Ndiye amene adachotsa anthu osakhulupirira amene adali pakati pa anthu a m’Buku kuchokera ku nyumba zawo pamene adakumana poyamba. Iwe sumaganiza ndi pang’ono pomwe kuti angachoke. Ndipo iwo anali kuganiza kuti Malinga awo adzawateteza kwa Mulungu! Koma chilango cha Mulungu chidadza pa iwo kuchokera kumbali imene iwo sanali kuyembekezera. Ndipo Iye adaika mantha m’mitima mwawo kotero iwo adagwetsa nyumba ndi manja awo ndiponso manja a anthu okhulupirira. Motero chenjerani tsopano inu amene muli ndi maso
  59,3,"Ngati Mulungu akadapanda kuwalamulira kuti achotsedwe, ndithudi, Iye akanawalanga m’dziko lomwe lino ndipo m’moyo umene uli nkudza, ndithudi, iwo adzalandira chilango cha ku Gahena"
  59,4,"Chifukwa iwo adatsutsa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi mwake. Ndipo ngati wina atsutsa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake, ndithudi, Mulungu ali ndi chilango choopsa"
  59,5,"Chilichonse chimene mudula cha mitengo ing’ono ing’ono ya tende kapena muisiya kuti ikhale njo pa mizu yake, mumachita ndi chilolezo cha Mulungu, ndi cholinga choti achititse manyazi anthu ochita zoipa"
  59,6,"Chimene Mulungu wapereka kwa Mtumwi wake ndipo walanda kuchokera kwa iwo, si ndinu amene mudapereka akabvalo kapena ngamira kwa iwo. Koma Mulungu ndiye amene amapereka mphamvu kwa Mtumwi wake kupambana aliyense amene iye wafuna ndipo Mulungu ali ndi mphamvu pa chilichonse"
  59,7,"Chilichonse chimene Mulungu wapereka ngati chuma chopeza pa nkhondo kwa Mtumwi wake, kuchokera kwa anthu a m’mizinda, mwini wakendi Mulungu, Mtumwiwakendiabalendiamasiye, ndi anthu osauka, ndi a paulendo ndi cholinga choti asakhale katundu wa anthu olemera amene ali pakati panu. Kotero landirani zimene Mtumwi akupatsani ndipo mulewe chimene akuletsani. Ndipo opani Mulungu. Ndithudi Mulungu amalanga molapitsa"
  59,8,"Ndi wa amphawi amene adabwera ndi Mtumwi amene adapilikitsidwa m’nyumba zawo ndi katundu wawo pofunafuna chisomo chochokera kwa Mulungu ndi chisangalalo chake. Ndipo amatsatira Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Amenewa, ndithudi, ndiwo olungama"
  59,9,"Ndipo iwo ndi amene, awa asadadze, adali ndi nyumba zawo ndipo adalowa Chisilamu, ndipo adaonetsa chikondi kwa iwo amene amadza kwa iwo, ndipo samachita kaduka ndi katundu amene aperekedwa kwa iwo koma amalolera kuti iwo akhale otsiliza polandira ngakhale kuti nawonso amazifuna. Ndipo aliyense amene amadziteteza ku zilakolako zake, ndithudi, iye adzakhala opambana"
  59,10,"Ndipo iwo amene adadza pambuyo pawo adati: “Ambuye wathu, tikhululukireni ife pamodzi ndi abale athu amene adalowa Chisilamu poyambirira, ndipo musasiye m’mitima mwathu kaduka wowachitira iwo amene adakhulupirira kale. Ambuye wathu! Ndithudi inu ndinu okoma mtima, Mwini chifundo.”"
  59,11,"Kodi iwe sudawaone anthu a chinyengo ali kunena kwa abale awo osakhulupirira amene ali pakati pa anthu a m’Buku? (Ponena kuti): “Ngati iwo akupirikitsani inu, nafenso tidzapita nanu, ndipo sitidzamvera wina aliyense wodana ndi inu. Ngati inu muputidwa, ndithudi, ife tidzakuthandizani.” Koma Mulungu achitira umboni kuti, ndithudi, iwo ndi abodza"
  59,12,"Ndithudi ngati iwo apirikitsidwa, iwo sadzapita nawo ayi ndipo ngati inu muputidwa iwo sadzakuthandizani konsekonse. Ndipo ngati iwo atathandiza, iwo adzangobwerera m’mbuyo motero iwo sadzapambana ai"
  59,13,Ndithudi inu mumayambitsa mantha m’mitima mwawo kuposa Mulungu. Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti iwo ndi anthu osazindikira
  59,14,Iwo sadzamenyana nawe ngati gulu limodzi ayi koma mozemba pogwiritsa ntchito Malinga ya m’mizinda kapena pobisala kuzipupa. Mtima womenya nkhondo ulipo pakati pawo moti iwe ukhoza kuganiza kuti ndi ogwirizana. Koma mitima yawo ndi yogawikana chifukwa iwo ndi anthu osadziwa chilichonse
  59,15,Iwo ali ngati amene adadza pambuyo pawo amene adalandira dipo loipa chifukwa cha ntchito zawo ndipo iwo adzalandira chilango chowawa kwambiri
  59,16,"Monga Satana pamene amamuuza munthu kuti: “Usakhulupirire mwa Mulungu.” Ndipo pamene munthu sakhulupirira mwa Mulungu, Satana amati: “Ndathana nawe tsopano chifukwa ine ndimaopa Mulungu, Ambuye wazolengedwa zonse.”"
  59,17,Motero mapeto awo ndi akuti onsewa adzapsa ku moto kumene adzakhalako mpaka kalekale. Limenelo ndilo dipo la anthu ochita zoipa
  59,18,oh inu anthu okhulupirira! opani Mulungu. Ndipo kwaniritsani udindo wanu kwa Iye. Ndipo ulekeni mzimu uliwonse uganize zimene udzalandire mawa ndipo opani Mulungu. Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  59,19,Ndipo inu musakhale ngati iwo amene adaiwala Mulungu ndipo Iye adawachititsa kuti adziiwale eni ake. Amenewa ndiwo amene amaphwanya malamulo mopitiriza
  59,20,Anthu a ku Gahena siofanana ndi anthu a ku Paradiso. Ndi anthu a ku Paradiso amene adzakhala opambana
  59,21,"Ife tikadatumiza Buku la Korani ili pa phiri, ndithudi; iwe ukadaona ilo lili kudzichepetsa ndi kung’ambika chifukwa cha mantha ndi Mulungu. Zimenezi ndi zitsanzo zimene timaulula kwa anthu kuti atha kuganiza"
  59,22,"Iye ndiye Mulungu ndipo kupatula Iye kulibe Mulungu wina amene amadziwa zinthu zonse zachinsinsi ndi zolankhula mokweza. Iye ndi Wachifundo, Mwini chisoni chosatha"
  59,23,"Iye ndiye Mulungu ndipo kupatula Iye kulibe Mulungu wina. Iye ndi Mwini Ufumu, Woyera, Maziko a mtendere, Mtetezi ndi Mwini ukulu. Ulemerero ukhale kwa Mulungu kuposa zimene amamusinjirira"
  59,24,"Iye ndi Mulungu, Namalenga, Chiyambi ndi Mkonzi. Ake ndi mayina abwino okhaokha. Chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi chimamulemekeza ndi kumuyamika ndipo Iye ndi Wolemekezeka, Wamphamvu ndi Wanzeru"
  60,1,"oh inu anthu amene mwakhulupirira! Musasandutse adani anga ndi adani anu kukhala abwenzi anu powaonetsa chikondi chanu pamene iwo akana choonadi chimene chadza kwa inu ndipo amupirikitsa Mtumwi pamodzi ndi inu nomwe kuchokera ku nyumba zanu, chifukwa chakuti inu mumakhulupirira mwa Mulungu Ambuye wanu. Ngati inu mwadza ndi cholinga chogwira ntchito m’njira yanga ndi kufunafuna chisangalalo changa(musachite nawo ubwenzi). Ndipo ngati inu mumaonetsa chikondi kwa iwo mwamseri, ndithudi, mukatero mwasochera. Ine ndimadziwa zonse zimene mumachita mseri"
  60,2,"Ngati iwo akupambanani, ndithudi, adzakuonetsani kuti ndi adani anu ndipo adzagwiritsa ntchito manja awo ndi malirime awo pa inu pokuchitirani zoipa. Iwo afunitsitsa kuti nanu mukhale anthu osakhulupirira"
  60,3,Abale anu kapena ana anu sadzakhala a phindu kwa inu patsiku la chiweruzo. Iye adzaweruza pakati panu chifukwa Mulungu amaona zonse zimene mumachita
  60,4,"Muli chitsanzo chabwino kwa inu mwa Abrahamu ndi mwa iwo amene adali naye pamene iwo ananena kwa anthu awo kuti: “Ife sitili m’gulu lanu ndipo sitipembedza zimene inu mumapembedza pozifanizira ndi Mulungu. Ife takukanani ndipo pabuka pakati pa ife ndi inu udani ndi chidani chosatha kupatula ngati inu mukhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi mwa Iye yekha.” Kupatula zonena za Abrahamu kwa Abambo ake kuti: “Ine ndidzapempha chikhululukiro chanu chifukwa ine ndilibe mphamvu pa chilichonse cha inu kuchokera kwa Mulungu. Ambuye wathu, mwa Inu ife takhulupirira ndi kwa Inu ndiko timapempha chikhululukiro, ndipo kwa Inu ndiko kumene tonse tidzabwerera pomaliza.”"
  60,5,"“Ambuye wathu, musatisandutse ife kukhala mayesero a anthu osakhulupirira koma tikhululukireni Ambuye wathu. Ndithudi Inu ndinu Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini nzeru zonse.”"
  60,6,"Ndithudi, mwa iwo mudali chitsanzo chabwino kwa inu kuti mutsatire, makamaka iwo amene amaika chikhulupiriro chawo mwa Mulungu ndi m’tsiku la chiweruzo. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wolemera ndipo ndiye yekha amene ayenera kulemekezedwa"
  60,7,Mwina Mulungu angakhazikitse chikondi pakati pa inu ndi iwo amene inu mumawaganizira kuti ndi adani anu. Ndithudi Mulungu ali ndi mphamvu pa china chilichonse ndipo Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  60,8,"Mulungu sali kukuletsani kuti muonetse chilungamo ndi chisoni kwa iwo amene sadamenyane nanu chifukwa cha chikhulupiliro chanu ndipo sanakuthamangitseni mu nyumba zanu. Ndithudi, Mulungu amakonda iwo amene amachita zolungama"
  60,9,Mulungu wakuletsani kuchita ubwenzi ndi anthu amene munamenyana nawo chifukwa cha chikhulupiriro ndipo anakuthamangitsani ku nyumba zanu kapena adathandiza anthu ena kuti amenyane ndi kukupirikitsani inu. Ndipo aliyense amene achita ubwenzi ndi anthu otere ndi ochimwa
  60,10,"Oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Pamene akazi okhulupirira adza kwa inu ngati othawa mavuto, afufuzeni bwinobwino. Mulungu yekha ndiye amene adziwa bwino bwino chikhulupiriro chawo. Ngati inu mukhutitsidwa kuti ndi okhulupirira m’choonadi, musawabwezere kwa anthu osakhulupirira chifukwa iwo saloledwa kukwatiwa ndi anthu osakhulupirira monga momwe amuna osakhulupirira saloledwa kukwatira akazi okhulupirira. Koma abwezereni anthu osakhulupirira ziwongo zimene apereka. Ndipo sikulakwa ngati inu muwakwatira akazi okhulupirirawa ngati mwapereka chiwongo. Musapitilize ukwati wanu ndi akazi wosakhulupirira. Itanitsani zimene mwaononga ngati chiwongo cha ukwati ndipo aloleni osakhulupirira kuti nawonso aitanitse zimene aononga pa akazi okhulupirira amene adza kwa inu. Ili ndi lamulo la Mulungu. Iye amaweruza mwachilungamo pakati panu. Mulungu ndi wa nzeru ndi luntha"
  60,11,"Ndipo ngati ena, mwa akazi anu, athawa ndi kukakwatiwa ndi osakhulupirira, ndipo inu mupeza mwayi wolandira akazi wochokera kwa anthu osakhulupirira abwezereni chiwongo ndi china chilichonse chimene iwo adapereka anthu amene akazi awo awathawa. Ndipo opani Mulungu amene inu mumamukhulupirira"
  60,12,"Oh iwe Mtumwi! Ngati akazi okhulupirira adza kwa iwe kudzalumbira lonjezo lakuti sadzamufanizira Mulungu ndi wina wake akamapembedza, kuti sadzaba, sadzachita chigololo, sadzapha ana awo, sadzalankhula mawu ojeda, sadzapeka nkhani zabodza ndipo kuti adzakumvera iwe pa nkhani ina iliyonse, iwe uyenera kulandira lonjezo lawo ndipo pempha kwa Mulungu kuti awakhululukire machimo awo chifukwa Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha"
  60,13,Oh inu okhulupirira! Musapalane ubwenzi ndi anthu amene adalandira mkwiyo wa Mulungu. Ndithudi iwo ali ndi mantha ndi zimene zidzawachitikira m’moyo umene uli nkudza monga momwe anthu osakhulupirira amachitira mantha ndi iwo amene adaikidwa m’manda
  61,1,"Chilichonse chimene chili mlengalenga ndi padziko lapansi, chimalemekeza Mulungu. Ndipo Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini nzeru"
  61,2,oh inu okhulupirira! Kodi bwanji mumanena zinthu zimene simuchita
  61,3,Ndithudi ndi chinthu chonyansa kwambiri pamaso pa Mulungu kuti muzinena chinthu chimene simuchita
  61,4,"Ndithudi Mulungu amakonda iwo amene amamenya nkhondo ndi cholinga chokhazikitsa ulamuliro wake molimba, m’magulu, ngati chipupa cha miyala"
  61,5,"Ndi pamene Mose adanena ndi anthu ake: “oh inu anthu anga! Kodi bwanji mukundikwiyitsa pamene muli kudziwa kuti ine ndine Mtumwi wa Mulungu kwa inuyo?” Ndipo pamene iwo adalakwa, Mulungu adalola kuti mitima yawo ilakwe. Ndipo Mulungu satsogolera anthu ophwanya malamulo"
  61,6,"Ndi pamene Yesu, mwana wa mwamuna wa Maria, adati: “oh inu ana a Israyeli! Ine ndine Mtumwi wa Mulungu amene ndatumidwa kwa inu, kutsimikizira za Buku la Chipangano chakale limene lidadza ine ndisanadze, ndi kuulula nkhani yabwino ya Mtumwi Ahmad amene adzabwera ine nditachoka.” Koma pamene iye adadza kwa iwo ndi zizindikiro zooneka, iwo adati: “Awa ndiwo matsenga enieni.”"
  61,7,"Kodi amalakwa kwambiri ndani kuposa As-Saff\t597 iye amene amapeka bodza lokhudza Mulungu ngakhale pamene ali kuitanidwa kuti alowe Chisilamu? Ndipo Mulungu satsogolera iwo amene amachita zoipa"
  61,8,Cholinga chawo ndikufuna kuzimitsa nyali ya Mulungu ndi milomo yawo. Koma Mulungu adzateteza nyali yake ngakhale kuti anthu osakhulupirira sakondwera nazo
  61,9,Ndiye amene watumiza Mtumwi wake ndi ulangizi ndiponso chipembedzo choonadi kuti chikhale chapamwamba pa zipembedzo zina zonse ngakhale kuti anthu osakhulupirira sakondwera nazo
  61,10,Oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Kodi ndikulangizeni malonda apafupi amene angakuomboleni ku chilango choopsa
  61,11,"Kuti mukhulupirire mwa Mulungu ndi mwa Mtumwi wake, kuti mudzipereke kwathunthu mu njira ya Mulungu pogwiritsa ntchito chuma chanu ndi inu eni ake. Chimenechi ndicho chinthu chabwino kwa inu ngati inu mukadadziwa"
  61,12,"Iyeadzakukhululukiraniinumachimoanu ndi kukulandirani m’minda imene pansi pake pamayenda mitsinje, ndipo adzakulowetsani m’nyumba zokongola ndi zaulemu za m’Paradiso. Kumeneko, ndithudi, ndiko kupambana kwenikweni"
  61,13,Ndipo Iye adzakupatsani madalitso ena amene mumakonda. Chithandizo chochokera kwa Mulungu ndi kupambana mwamsanga. Kotero auze nkhani yabwino anthu okhulupirira
  61,14,"oh inu okhulupirira! Khalani otumikira Mulungu monga momwe ananenera Yesu, mwana wa mwamuna wa Maria, kwa ophunzira ake: “Kodi ndani andithandiza ine potumikira Mulungu?” Iwo adayankha: “Ife ndife othandiza Mulungu.” Kotero ena mwa ana a Israyeli adakhulupirira pamene ena sadakhulupirire. Motero Ife tidawapatsa mphamvu iwo amene adakhulupirira zopambana adani awo ndipo iwo adapambanadi"
  62,1,"Chilichonse chimene chili mlengalenga ndi padziko lapansi chimatamanda ndi kulemekeza Mulungu, Mfumu ya Mafumu, Woyera, Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini nzeru"
  62,2,"Ndiye amene adatumiza kugulu la anthu osaphunzira Mtumwi, wochokera m’gulu lawo, kuwauza iwo zizindikiro zake, kuwayeretsa ndi kuwaphunzitsa Buku. Ndithudi iwo anali kuchita zoipa kuyambira kale"
  62,3,Ndipo Iye wamutumiza iye pamodzi ndi ena amene anali pakati pawo amene sadalowe m’gulu lawo. Ndipo Iye ndi Wamphamvu ndi Wanzeru
  62,4,Chimenchi ndicho chisomo cha Mulungu chimene amachipereka kwa aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Ndipo Mulungu ndiye Ambuye wachisomo chapamwamba chosatha
  62,5,"Fanizo la iwo amene adapatsidwa Buku la Chipangano Chakale ndipo adalephera kukwaniritsa malamulo ake, lili ngati Bulu amene amasenza katundu wambiri wolemera wa mabuku. Loipa ndi fanizo la anthu amene amakana zizindikiro za Mulungu. Ndipo Mulungu satsogolera anthu ochita zoipa"
  62,6,"Nena: “oh inu Ayuda! Ngati inu mumaganiza kuti inu nokha ndinu abwenzi a Mulungu Al Jumua\t599 kusiyana ndi anthu ena, pemphani imfa kuti idze pa inu ngati ndinu a chilungamo"
  62,7,Koma iwo sadzaipempha iyo chifukwa cha ntchito zimene manja awo adachita. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa onse amene amachita zoipa
  62,8,"Nena: “Ndithudi imfa imene muli kuopa, ndithudi, idzadza pa inu ndipo inu mudzabwerera kwa Iye amene amadziwa zinthu zonse zobisika ndi zooneka ndipo Iye adzakuuzani zonse zimene munali kuchita"
  62,9,"Oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Ngati mumva kuitana kwa mapemphero a masana a tsiku lachisanu, fulumirani kukakumbukira Mulungu ndipo siyani ntchito zanu. Chimenechondichochabwinokwainungatimukadadziwa"
  62,10,"Ndipo ngati mapemphero akutha, mukhoza kumwazikana, padziko kukafunafuna zokoma za Mulungu ndipo muzikumbukira Mulungu kwambiri kuti mukhale opambana"
  62,11,"Ndipo iwo akaona katundu wa malonda kapena zinthu zina zosangalatsa, iwo amazithamangira izo ndi kukusiya wekha uli chiimire pa mapamphero. Nena: “Zimene Mulungu ali nazo ndi zabwino kwambiri kuposa katundu wina aliyense wamalonda kapena chisangalalo.” Mulungu ndiye amene amapereka moolowa manja"
  63,1,"Pamene anthu a chinyengo amadza kwa iwe amati: “Ife tichitira umboni kuti iwe, ndithudi, ndiwe Mtumwi wa Mulungu. Inde Mulungu amadziwa kuti iwe, ndithudi, ndiwe Mtumwi wake ndipo Mulungu achitira umboni kuti anthu achinyengo, ndithudi, ndi abodza"
  63,2,Iwo asandutsa malonjezo awo ngati tchingo. Motero iwo amaletsa anthu ena kuti atsatire njira ya Mulungu. Ndithudi zimene iwo amachita ndi zoipa
  63,3,Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti iwo adakhulupirirapoyambandipopambuyopakeadayambanso kusakhulupirira. Motero mitima yawo idatsekedwa ndipo sazindikira china chilichonse
  63,4,"Ndipo pamene iwe uwaona, matupi awo amakusangalatsa ndipo pamene iwo alankhula, iwe umamvera zonena zawo. Iwo ali ngati matabwa amene aimikidwa pa chipupa. Iwo amaganiza kuti mawu onse amene amveka amanena za iwo. Iwo ndi adani kotero chenjera nawo. Matemberero a Mulungu akhale pa iwo! Kodi iwo asocheretsedwa bwanji kunjira yoyenera"
  63,5,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Bwerani kuti mwina Mtumwi wa Mulungu akupemphereni chikhululukiro kuchokera kwa Mulungu, ” iwo amabwerera m’mbuyo ndipo iwe umawaona ali kutembenuza nkhope zawo mwachipongwe"
  63,6,"Ndi chimodzimodzi kwa iwo kaya iwe uwapemphera chikhululukiro kapena ayi Mulungu sadzawakhululukira Al Munafiqun\t601 iwo. Ndithudi Mulungu satsogolera anthu ophwanya malamulo"
  63,7,"Iwo ndiwo amene amati: “Musawapatse china chilichonse anthu amene ali ndi Mtumwi wa Mulungu kuti amuthawe.” Koma Mulungu ndiye Mwini wa chuma cha mlengalenga ndi padziko lapansi koma anthu achinyengo sadziwa zimenezi"
  63,8,"Iwo amati: “Ngati tibwerera ku Medina, ndithudi, anthu a mphamvu, adzathamangitsa anthu kuchoka ku Mzindawo.” Koma ulemu, mphamvu ndi ulemerero ndi wa Mulungu, Mtumwi wake ndi okhulupilira koma anthu a chinyengo sadziwa chimenechi"
  63,9,"oh inu okhulupirira! Musalole chuma kapena ana anu kuti akusokonezeni pokukumbukira Mulungu. Ndipo aliyense amene achita motero, ndithudi, ndi wotayika"
  63,10,"Ndipo perekani kuchokera ku katundu amene takupatsani imfa isanadze pa wina wa inu kuti iye asanene kuti: “Oh Ambuye wanga! Inu mukadandibweza mwa kanthawi kochepa, ine ndikadapereka chaulere chochuluka kuchokera ku chuma changa ndikukhala mmodzi wa anthu ochita zabwino.”"
  63,11,Ndipo Mulungu sapereka nthawi kwa wina pamene nthawi yake itakwana. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  64,1,Chilichonse chili mlengalenga ndi padziko lapansi chimatamanda ndi kulemekeza Mulungu. Iye ndiye Mwini ufumu ndipo kwake ndi kuyamikidwa ndipo Iye ali ndi mphamvu pa chilichonse
  64,2,Ndiye amene adakulengani inu ndipo ena a inu ndi osakhulupirira pamene ena ndi okhulupirira. Mulungu amaona zonse zimene mumachita
  64,3,Iye adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi mwa chilungamo ndipo Iye adakulengani ndi kukupatsani maonekedwe abwino ndipo kwa Iye ndi kumene mudzabwerera
  64,4,Iye amadziwa chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi ndipo amadziwa zonse zimene mumabisa ndi zimene mumaulula. Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa bwino lomwe zinsinsi za m’mitima mwanu
  64,5,"Kodi inu simudamve za iwo amene sadakhulupirire kale? Ndipo iwo adalawa chilango chifukwa chosakhulupilira, ndipo chawo chidzakhala chilango chowawa kwambiri"
  64,6,"Ichi ndi chifukwa chakuti kunadza kwa iwo Atumwi amene adali ndi zizindikiro zooneka koma iwo adati: “Kodi ife tizitsogozedwa ndi anthu anzathu?” Kotero iwo sanakhulupilire ndipo anabwerera m’mbuyo. Koma Mulungu sasowa kanthu. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi Mwini wa chilichonse ndi Mwini ulemerero wonse. Al Taghabun"
  64,7,"Anthu osakhulupirira amaganiza kuti sadzaukitsidwa kwa akufa. Nena: “Inde! Pali Ambuye wanga! Inu, ndithudi, mudzaukitsidwa kwa akufa ndipo mudzauzidwa zimene mudachita. Zimenezo ndi za pafupi ndi Mulungu.”"
  64,8,Motero khulupirirani mwa Mulungu ndi mwa Mtumwi wake ndi mu Muuni umene Ife tatumiza. Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  64,9,"Patsiku limene Iye adzakusonkhanitsani inu nonse, tsiku losonkhana, tsiku limeneli lidzakhala tsiku la mavuto ndi la mtendere kwa ena a inu. Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino, Iye adzawakhululukira machimo awo ndipo adzawaika m’minda imene imathiriridwa ndi mitsinje yoyenda madzi pansi pake kuti akhale m’menemo mpaka kalekale. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwenikweni"
  64,10,"Koma iwo amene sakhulupirira ndipo amakana ulangizi wathu, iwo adzakhala ku moto nthawi zonse omwe ndi malo oipitsitsa kukhalako"
  64,11,"Palibe vuto limene limadza popanda chilolezo cha Mulungu ndipo aliyense amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu, Iye amatsogolera mtima wake ndipo Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse"
  64,12,"Mverani Mulungu ndipo mverani Mtumwi wake. Koma ngati inu mukana, udindo wa Mtumwi wathu ndi kukuuzani uthenga wathu momveka ndi poyera"
  64,13,Mulungu! Kulibe Mulungu wina koma Iye yekha ndipo mwa Mulungu onse okhulupirira aike chikhulupiriro chawo
  64,14,"Oh inu okhulupirira! Ndithudi pakati pa akazi ndi ana anu alipo ena amene ndi adani anu, motero chenjerani! Koma ngati inu muwakhululukira ndipo simulabadira zoipa zawo, ndithudi, Mulungu ndi wokhululukira nthawi zonse ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha"
  64,15,Chuma chanu ndipo ana anu ndi mayesero pamene Mulungu ndiye amene ali ndi mphotho yaikulu
  64,16,Kotero kwaniritsani udindo wanu kwa Mulungu ndipo muopeni Iye kwambiri. Mverani ndipo mumvere. Ndipo perekani chopereka chaulere. Chimenecho ndi chabwino kwa inu. Ndipo aliyense amene asiya umbombo adzakhala wopambana
  64,17,"Ngati mukongoza Mulungu ngongole yabwino, Iye adzaichulukitsa ndipo adzakukhululukirani machimo anu. Ndipo Mulungu ndi wokonzeka kuyamika ndi kulipira ndipo ndi wopilira kwambiri"
  64,18,Wodziwa zonse zobisika ndi zooneka ndipo ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini nzeru zonse
  65,1,"Oh iwe Mtumwi! Ngati usudzula akazi ako, asudzule potsatira nthawi zawo. Ndipo werenga bwino bwino masiku awo. Ndipo opani Mulungu Ambuye wanu ndipo musawapirikitse m’nyumba zawo ndipo iwo asachoke pokhapokha ngati iwo apalamula mlandu wachigololo. Amenewa ndiwo malamulo amene akhazikitsidwa ndi Mulungu. Ndipo aliyense amene aphwanya malamulo a Mulungu, ndithudi, amapondereza mzimu wake. Inu Al Talaq\t605 simudziwa kuti, mwina, Mulungu adzakukumanizaninso"
  65,2,"Ndipo ngati iwo ali pafupi kukwaniritsa nthawi yawo, mukhoza kuwasunga mwaubwino kapena kuwasiya mwaulemu. Ndipo itanani mboni ziwiri za chilungamo kuchokera pakati panu. Ndipo perekani umboni wanu chifukwa cha Mulungu. Limeneli ndi langizo limene laperekedwa kwa iye amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi tsiku lomaliza. Ndipo aliyense amene aopa Mulungu, Iye adzamupulumutsa"
  65,3,"Ndipo Iye adzamupatsa zinthu kuchokera ku mbali imene sanali kuyembekeza. Ndipo aliyense amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu, Iye adzamupatsa chili chonse. Mulungu, ndithudi, adzamupatsa iye zofuna zake zonse. Ndithudi Mulungu adakhazikitsa muyeso wa chilichonse"
  65,4,"Ndipo ena akazi anu amene adasiya kupita kumwezi, kwa iwo nthawi yawo yodikira, ngati inu mukaika, ndi miyezi itatu ndipo iwo amene anasiyiratu, nthawi yawo idzakhala chimodzimodzi. Ndipo iwo amene ali ndi akazi odwala pakati, nthawi yawo idzakhala mpaka pamene abereka. Ndipo aliyense amene amaopa Mulungu, Iye adzamuchepetsera mavuto ake"
  65,5,"Uwu ndi ulamuliro wa Mulungu umene wakutumizirani inu. Ndipo aliyense amene aopa Mulungu, Iye adzamuchotsera zoipa zake. Ndipo Iye adzamuchulukitsira mphotho yake"
  65,6,"Khalani nawo monga momwe inu muli kukhalira, molingana ndi kupeza kwanu. Musawazunze ndi cholinga chowasowetsa mtendere. Ngati iwo ali ndi pakati, asamalireni mpaka pamene iwo abereka. Ndipo ngati iwo ali kuyamwitsa, apatseni malipiro awo ndipo lemekezanani. Ndipo ngati pali mavuto oti simuli kugwirizana m’banja, pezani Mayi wina kuti ayamwitse mwana m’malo mwake"
  65,7,Mulekeni munthu wolemera kuti apereke molingana ndi chuma chake ndipo munthu wosauka molingana ndi mmene Mulungu adamupatsira iye. Mulungu sakhazika mtulo wolemera pa munthu umene sangathe kuunyamula. Mulungu adzapereka mtendere mavuto akatha
  65,8,Ndipo ndi mizinda yambiri imene idaukira malamulo a Mulungu ndi Atumwi ndipo Ife tidayilanga iyo ndipo tidzailanga ndi chilango choopsa zedi
  65,9,Motero iyo idalawa mphotho ya kusakhulupilira kwake ndipo mapeto a kusakhulupilira adali chionongeko
  65,10,"Mulungu wawakonzeraiwochilangochoopsa. Moteroopani Mulungu oh inu anthu ozindikira! Inu amene mwakhulupirira, ndithudi, Mulungu watumiza chikumbutso kwa inu"
  65,11,"Mtumwi amene ali kukuuzani zizindikiro zooneka za Mulungu ndi cholinga choti atsogolere onse amene akhulupirira ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino kuchokera ku mdima kupita kowala. Ndipo aliyense amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino, Iye adzamulowetsa m’minda imene pansi pake pamayenda mitsinje kuti adzakhaleko mpaka kalekale. Ndithudi Mulungu wawapatsa iwo mphotho yabwino kwambiri"
  65,12,Ndi Mulungu amene adalenga miyamba isanu ndi iwiri ndi dziko lapansi lolingana nayo. Malamulo ake amatsatiridwa ndi izo kuti inu mukhoza kudziwa kuti Mulungu ali ndi mphamvu pa zinthu zonse ndipo kuti Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse
  66,1,"Oh iwe Mtumwi! Bwanji ukudziletsa zinthu zimene Mulungu adakuloleza kuti uchite ndipo iwe ufuna kukondweretsa akazi ako? Ndipo Mulungu ndi wokhululukira nthawi zonse, Mwini chisoni chosatha"
  66,2,"Mulungu wakulolezani kuti mukhoza kumasula malonjezo anu. Ndipo Mulungu ndiye Mtetezi wanu, ndipo ndi wodziwa ndi Mwini nzeru zonse"
  66,3,"Ndi pamene Mtumwi anamuuza nkhani ya chinsinsi wina wa akazi ake ndipo iye adaulula kwa mnzake wina ndipo Mulungu adamuuza iye za izo, Iye anamuuza gawo la nkhani ndipo anasiya gawo lina. Ndipo pamene iye adamuuza mkaziyo za izo, iye adati: “Ndani wakuuzani izi?” Iye adati: “Wandiuza ndi amene amadziwa chilichonse ndi Mwini kuzindikira.”"
  66,4,"Ngati inu awiri mulapa machimo anu kwa Mulungu ndipo mitima yanu itsimikiza kutero, koma ngati inu mugwirizana kulimbana naye, ndithudi, Mulungu ndiye Mtetezi wake, ndi Gabriele ndipo aliyense wolungama amene ali pakati pa anthu amene akhulupirira ndi angelo. Onse ndi omuthandiza iye"
  66,5,"Zingatheke kuti pamene iye akusudzulani inu, Mulungu adzamupatsa m’malo mwanu, akazi ena abwino oposa inu amene amadzipereka kwa Mulungu, amene ali okhulupirira, opirira, olapa kwa Mulungu, opembedza modzichepetsa, osala zifuniro zawo, kapena obwera amene anakwatiwapo kale kapena a namwali"
  66,6,"oh inu okhulupirira! Dzitetezeni nokha ndi mabanja anu ku moto umene nkhuni zake ndi anthu ndi miyala ndipo oyang’anira ake ndi angelo a mphamvu a maonekedwe oopsa amene sakana kumvera malamulo amene amalandira kuchokera kwa Mulungu ndipo amachita, mwamsanga, chilichonse chimene Mulungu wawalamula"
  66,7,oh inu osakhulupirira! Musawiringule lero! Inu muli kulandira mphotho yolingana ndi zimene mudachita
  66,8,"oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Lapani kwa Mulungu mwachoonadi! Mwina Ambuye wanu angakuchotserani machimo anu ndi kukulowetsani inu m’minda imene pansi pake pamayenda mitsinje. Tsiku limene Mulungu sadzalola kuti Mtumwi ndi iwo amene amamutsatira kuti azunzidwe, nyali yawo idzayaka patsogolo pawo ndi Buku ku dzanja lamanja lawo. Iwo adzati: “Ambuye wathu walitsani nyali yathu ndipo tikhululukireni. Ndithudi inu muli ndi mphamvu pa zinthu zonse.”"
  66,9,"oh iwe Mtumwi! Limbika kwambiri pogonjetsa anthu osakhulupirira ndi anthu a chinyengo ndipo chita nawo mwankhanza, malo awo ndi kumoto, omwe ndi malo oipa kwambiri kukhalako"
  66,10,"Mulungu ali kupereka chitsanzo kwa anthu osakhulupirira cha nkhani ya mkazi wa Nowa ndi mkazi wa Loti. Iwo adali akazi a Atumiki athu awiri a ngwiro, koma onse adanyenga amuna awo. Iwo sadalandire kuchokera kwa Mulungu chabwino china chilichonse chifukwa chamakhalidwe awo. Koma iwo adauzidwa kuti: “Lowani inu kumoto pamodzi ndi ena amene ali kulowako.”"
  66,11,"Ndipo Mulungu wapereka chitsanzo kwa anthu okhulupirira, nkhani ya mkazi wa Farao. Pamene iye adati: “oh Ambuye wanga! Ndimangireni pafupi ndi Inu, nyumba ya ulemu ku Paradiso, ndipo ndipulumutseni kwa Farao ndi ntchito zake ndipo ndipulumutseni ine kwa athu amene amachita zoipa.”"
  66,12,"Ndi Maria mwana wa Imran, amene adadzisunga wosadulaunamwaliwakendipo Ifetidauziram’thupimwake mzimu wathu ndipo Iye adachitira umboni wachilungamo cha Ambuye wake ndi chivumbulutso chake. Ndipo iye adali mmodzi wa odzipereka kwa Mulungu"
  67,1,wodalitsika ndiye amene mmanja mwake muli Ufumu ndipo ali ndi mphamvu pa zinthu zonse
  67,2,Iye amene adalenga imfa ndi moyo kuti akhoza kukuyesani inu kuti ndani wa inu amene wasunga malamulo onse mwaubwino. Ndipo Iye ndi Wamphamvu ndi Wokhululukira
  67,3,"Iye ndi amene adalenga miyamba isanu ndi iwiri, wina pamwamba pa unzake. Inu simungaone cholakwa china chilichonse mu chilengedwe cha Mwini chisoni chosatha. Tapenyetsetsani! Kodi inu mungaone cholakwika china chilichonse"
  67,4,Tapenyetsetsaninso! Ndipo mawonekedwe anu adzakubwererani pamene ali osokonezeka ndi otopa
  67,5,Ndithudi Ife takongoletsa thambo loyamba ndi nyali ndipo tazipanga nyalizo ngati mipaliro yothamangitsira Satana ndipo tawakonzera iwo chilango chamoto woyaka
  67,6,"Ndipo iwo amene sakhulupirira mwa Ambuye wawo, kuli chilango cha kumoto ndipo chimaliziro chawo chidzakhala choipa"
  67,7,"Ndipo pamene iwo adzaponyedwa m’moto, iwo adzaumva uli kuyaka ndi kubwata"
  67,8,"Pafupifupi kuphulika chifukwa cha kukwiya. Ndipo nthawi zonse pamene gulu liponyedwamo, amene amayang’anira moto adzafunsa kuti: “Kodi panalibe wina aliyense amene adadza kwa inu kudzakuchenjezani?”"
  67,9,"Ndipo iwo adzati: “Inde. Ndithudi Mchenjezi adadza kwa ife koma tidamukana ndipo tinkati: Mulungu sadavumbulutse china chilichonse ndipo iwe ndiwe wosokoneza kwambiri.”"
  67,10,"Ndipo iwo adzati: “Tikadakhala kuti tidamvera kapena kuganiza bwino, ife sitikadakhala m’gulu la anthu opita ku moto.”"
  67,11,Motero iwo adzabvomera machimo awo. Motero apite kutali anthu a ku moto
  67,12,"Ndithudi! Iwo amene amaopa Ambuye wawo ngakhale samuona, ndithudi, iwo adzawakhululukira machimo awo ndipo adzalandira mphotho ya mtengo wapatali"
  67,13,"Ndipo kaya mubisa mawu anu kapena muulula, Iye amadziwa zonse zimene zili m’mitima mwanu"
  67,14,Kodi Iye amene adalenga zinthu zonse asadziwe? Ndithudi Iye ndi wa Chisoni chosatha ndi Mwini kudziwa chili chonse
  67,15,"Iye ndiye amene anakukonzerani dziko, motero pitani paliponse mu ilo, ndipo idyani zokoma zake zimene wakupatsanindipondikwaIyekumenezonsezidzabwerera"
  67,16,Kodi inu mumaganiza kuti ndinu wokhazikika moti Iye amene ali pamwamba pa kumwamba sangathe kung’amba nthaka imene ili pansi panu kuti ikumezeni? Taonani! Ili kugwedezeka
  67,17,Kapena mumaganiza kuti inu ndinu okhazikika kuposa zimene zili kumwamba kuti Iye sangathe kukutumizirani mphepo ya mkuntho? Kotero inu mudzadziwa kuopsa kwa chenjezo langa
  67,18,Ndithudi iwo amene adalipo kale anakana. Kodi chilango changa chinali bwanji
  67,19,"Kodiiwosaonambalamezimenezimaulukapamwamba pawo, zikutambasula ndi kutseka mapiko awo? Palibe chimene chimazigwira kupatula Mwini chisoni chosatha. Ndithudi Iye amaona chilichonse"
  67,20,Kodi ndani amene angakuthandizeni inu kupatula Mwini chisoni chosatha? Anthu onse osakhulupirira ndi olakwa
  67,21,Kodi ndani amene angakupatseni chisamaliro ngati Iye atakaniza chisamaliro chake? Koma iwo amapitiriza kuchita mtudzu ndi kugalukira
  67,22,Kodi iye amene amayenda osaona ndi ofanana ndi amene walangizidwa kapena amene amayenda mu njira yoyenera
  67,23,"Nena: “Ndiye amene adakulengani inu ndipo adakupatsani makutu, maso ndi mitima. Inu simuthokoza kawirikawiri.”"
  67,24,"Nena: “Ndiye amene anakulengani inu kuchokera ku doti ndipo kwa Iye nonse mudzasonkhanitsidwa.”"
  67,25,"Iwo amati: “Kodi lonjezo limeneli lidzakwaniritsidwa liti ngati zimene ulikunena ndi zoona?”"
  67,26,"Nena: “Mulungu yekha ndiye amene adziwa nthawi yake. Ntchito yanga ndikungokuchenjezani basi.”"
  67,27,"Koma pamene iwo adzachiona chili nkudza pafupi, nkhope za anthu osakhulupirira zidzakhala za chisoni ndipo kudzanenedwa kuti: “Ichi ndi chimaliziro chimene munkafunsa kuti chidzafika liti?”"
  67,28,"Nena: “Ndiuzeni! Kodi ngati Mulungu atandiononga ine pamodzi ndi iwo amene ali nane, ngakhale kuti Iye adzaonetsa chifundo pa ife, ndani amene angateteze anthu osakhulupirira ku chilango chowawa?”"
  67,29,"Nena: “Iye ndi Mwini chifundo chosatha, mwa Iye ife timakhulupirira ndipo mwa Iye ife timaika chikhulupiriro chathu. Kotero inu mudzadziwa posachedwapa kuti ndani amene ali wochimwa.”"
  67,30,"Nena: “Ndiuzeni! Kodi ngati madzi anu ataphwa, ndani amene angakupatseni inu madzi oyenda?”"
  68,1,Nun. Pali cholembera ndi zimene amalemba
  68,2,"Mwachisomo cha Ambuye wako, sindiwe wamisala ayi"
  68,3,Ndithudi iwe udzalandira mphotho yosatha
  68,4,Ndithudi iwe uli ndi makhalidwe abwino
  68,5,Iwe udzaona ndipo nawo adzaona
  68,6,Kuti ndani wa inu amene ndi wamisala
  68,7,Ndithudi Ambuye wako amadziwa bwino amene wasochera ku njira yake ndipo amadziwa bwino amene amayenda m’njira yoyenera
  68,8,Motero usatsatire zochita za anthu osakhulupirira
  68,9,Iwo afuna utagwirizana nawo kuti nawonso agwirizane nawe
  68,10,Ndipo usamvere zonena za munthu wotukwana amene alibe phindu
  68,11,"Woononga mbiri ya anzake ponena Al Qalam\t613 za bodza"
  68,12,"Woletsa ntchito zachilungamo, wophwanya malamulo ndi wochita zoipa"
  68,13,woipa mtima ndipo wobadwa mosalongosoka
  68,14,Chifukwa iye ali ndi chuma ndi ana
  68,15,"Pamene chivumbulutso chathu chilakatulidwa kwa iye, amati: “Ndi nkhani za anthu a makedzana.”"
  68,16,Ife tidzaika chizindikiro pa mphuno pake
  68,17,"Ndithudi Ife tidawayesa iwo monga momwe tidawayesera eni ake a munda, amene adalumbira kuti adzakolola mbewu zawo m’mawa mwake"
  68,18,"Osaonjezera mawu oti: “Ngati Mulungu alola.”"
  68,19,Kotero kudadutsa china chake chochokera kwa Ambuye wako nthawi ya usiku ndi kuwotcha pamene iwo anali kugona
  68,20,"Ndipo m’mawa, munda udasanduka wakuda monga mdima wa usiku"
  68,21,Ndipo mmawa iwo adaitanizana wina ndi mnzake
  68,22,"Nati: “Mulawirire ku munda ngati mufuna kukakolola.”"
  68,23,"Ndipo iwo adapita, namanong’onezana wina ndi mnzake"
  68,24,“Palibe munthu wosauka amene adzaloledwa kulowa m’mundamo kudzapempha”
  68,25,"Ndipo m’mawa, onse adapita ndi mphamvu zotchinjirizira anthu osauka"
  68,26,"Koma pamene iwo adaona zimene zidachitika, onse adati: “Ndithudi ife talakwa.”"
  68,27,“Iai! Ndithudi ife tapwetekeka.”
  68,28,"wangwiro amene anali pakati pawo adati: “Kodi ine sindidakuuzeni kuti bwanji inu simunena kuti: Ngati Mulungu alola?”"
  68,29,“Iwo adati ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wathu! Ndithudi ife ndife olakwa.”
  68,30,Ndipo iwo adayamba kudzudzulana kuti wina adali wolakwa
  68,31,"Iwo adati: “Tsoka kwa ife! Ndithudi Ife tidali ophwanya malamulo.”"
  68,32,“Mwina kuti Ambuye wathu adzatipatsa munda wina wabwino m’malo mwa uwu. Ndithudi ndi kwa Iye kumene timapempha modzichepetsa.”
  68,33,"Chimenechi ndicho chilango koma ndithudi chilango cha m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndi chowawa kwambiri, iwo akadadziwa"
  68,34,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzalandira minda ya madalitso imene ili ndi Ambuye wawo
  68,35,Kodi Ife tidzasamala anthu angwiro chimodzimodzi ndi anthu ochimwa
  68,36,Kodi mwatani? Kodi inu mumaweruza bwanji
  68,37,Kapena kodi muli ndi Buku limene mumawerengamo
  68,38,Kuti inu mudzapeza m’menemo chilichonse chimene mukufuna
  68,39,"Kapena inu mwalandira kuchokera kwa Ife, lonjezo lotsimikizika mpaka pa tsiku louka kwa akufa kuti, ndithudi, inu mudzapeza zimene mukufuna"
  68,40,Tawafunsa ngati wina wa iwo angachitire umboni za lonjezolo
  68,41,"Kapena, kodi iwo ali ndi milungu ina? Aleke abweretse milungu yawo ngati iwo anena zoona"
  68,42,"Ndipatsikulimenechinthuchoopsachidzachitika, iwo adzaitanidwa kuti apembedze, koma adzalephera kutero"
  68,43,Maso awo adzayang’ana pansi ndipo adzanyozedwa kwambiri chifukwa iwo adauzidwa kupembedza pamene adali pa mtendere
  68,44,Kotero ndisiyire aliyense amene akutsutsana ndi chenjezo ili. Ife tidzawalanga pang’onopang’ono m’njira imene iwo saizindikira
  68,45,Ndipo Ine ndidzalekerera pa kanthawi! Ndithudi chikonzero changa ndi champhamvu
  68,46,Kapena kodi iwe uli kuwafunsa malipiro moti iwo ali ndi ngongole yambiri
  68,47,Kapena kodi iwo amadziwa za Buku lobisika kuti iwo akhoza kulemba
  68,48,Motero pirira podikilira chiweruzo cha Ambuye wako ndipo usakhale ngati amene adamezedwa ndi nsomba pamene adalira kupempha chithandizo iye ali m’mavuto
  68,49,"Ngati Ambuye wake akadapanda kumuonetsa chisomo chake, ndithudi iye akadakhalabe koma iye adaponyedwa pa mtunda pamene anali wolakwa"
  68,50,Koma Ambuye wake adamusankha ndipo adamuchititsa kukhala wabwino
  68,51,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo onse osakhulupirira akadakusokeretsa ndi maso awo pamene amakumbutsidwa ndipo amati: “Ndithudi uyu ndi Wamisala.”"
  68,52,Koma ichi si china koma chikumbutso kwa zolengedwa zonse
  69,1,Choonadi chenicheni
  69,2,Kodi choonadi chenicheni ndi chiyani
  69,3,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chingakupangitse kuti udziwe kuti choonadi chenicheni ndi chiti
  69,4,Mtundu wa Thamoud ndi Ad adakana ola la chionongeko
  69,5,Ndipo anthu a Thamoud adaonongeka ndi mfuwu woopsya
  69,6,Ndipo anthu a Aad adaonongeka ndi chimphepo cha mkuntho
  69,7,Chimene Mulungu adachilamulira kuti chikunthe pa iwo usiku usanu ndi uwiri ndi usana usanu ndi utatu mosalekeza. Moti iwe ukadawaona anthu atagonagona ukadayesa kuti ndi mitengo ya migwalangwa yakugwa
  69,8,Kodi uli kuona wina wa iwo opulumuka
  69,9,"Ndipo Farao ndi anthu amene adalipo iye asadabadwe, ndi a mizinda imene idaonongeka anali kuchita zoipa"
  69,10,Ndipo iwo sanamvere Mtumwi wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo ndipo Iye adawalanga ndi chilango chowawa zedi
  69,11,"Ndithudi!Pamenemadzianasefukira,Ifetidakunyamulani inu m’chombo"
  69,12,Kuti tikhoza kuchipanga icho kukhala chikumbutso ndi kuti khutu la kumva limve
  69,13,Ndipo pamene lipenga lidzaimbidwa kamodzi
  69,14,Ndipo nthaka ndi mapiri anyamulidwa pamodzi ndi kuponyedwa pansi mwamphamvu kamodzi
  69,15,Patsiku limeneli chinthu choopsa chidzachitika
  69,16,Ndipo thambo lidzaphwanyika ndipo lidzakhala lopanda mphamvu
  69,17,Ndipo Angelo adzaima mbali zonse ndipo angelo asanu ndi atatu pa tsikuli adzanyamula Mpando wa Chifumu wa Ambuye wako
  69,18,Patsiku limeneli mudzaweruzidwa ndipo palibe chinthu chachinsinsi chimene chidzabisika
  69,19,"Ndipo yense amene adzapatsidwa Buku lake kudzanja lamanja adzati: “Ah taonani! Werengani Buku langa!”"
  69,20,"Ndithudi, ine ndidakhululupira kuti tsiku lina zochita zanga zidzaweruzidwa"
  69,21,Kotero iye adzakhala ndi moyo wa chisangalalo
  69,22,M’munda wapamwamba
  69,23,Wa zipatso zokoma zimene zili pafupi
  69,24,Idyani ndipo imwani mmene mufunire chifukwa cha ntchito zanu zabwino zimene mudatumiza patsogolo panu m’masiku apitawo
  69,25,"Koma iye amene adzapatsidwe buku lake m’dzanja lamanzere, adzati: “Kukadakhala bwino ngati Buku langa likadakhala losaperekedwa kwa ine.”"
  69,26,“Ndipo sindikadziwa kuti zochita zanga zachuluka bwanji.”
  69,27,“Ikadakhala bwino imfa ikadangodza pa ine.”
  69,28,“Chuma changa sichidandithandize chilichonse.”
  69,29,“Ulamuliro wanga wonse wachoka kwa ine.”
  69,30,“Mugwireni ndipo mumumange.”
  69,31,“Ndipo m’ponyeni M’ng’anjo ya moto.”
  69,32,“Ndipo mumangeni ndi unyolo wotalika malipande makumi asanu ndi awiri.”
  69,33,"Ndithudi, iye samakhulupirira mwa Mulungu wamkulu"
  69,34,Ndipo sadali kuthandiza kudyetsa anthu osowa
  69,35,Motero lero iye sadzakhala ndi bwenzi aliyense
  69,36,Kapena chakudya china chilichonse kupatula zonyasa zochoka pa zilonda
  69,37,Palibe amene adzachidya kupatula ochimwa ndi osakhulupilira
  69,38,Motero Ine ndilumbira pali chilichonse chimene uli nkuona
  69,39,Ndi chimene chili chobisika
  69,40,Kuti ndithudi awa ndi mawu a Mtumwi wolemekezeka
  69,41,Ndipo si mawu a Mlakatuli ayi ndipo chikhulupiriro chanu ndi chochepa
  69,42,"Ndipo si mawu a munthu wa maula ayi, ndipo ndi zochepa zimene inu mukumbukira"
  69,43,Ichi ndi chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  69,44,Ndipo iye akanapeka nkhani yokhudza Ife
  69,45,Ndithudi Ife tikadagwira dzanja lake lamanja
  69,46,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ifetikadadulamtsemphawakewamoyo"
  69,47,"Ndipo palibe, wina wa inu, amene akadatiletsa Ife kumugwira"
  69,48,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Korani iyi ndi chikumbutso kwa iwo amene amapewa zoipa"
  69,49,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife timadziwa kuti alipo ena a inu amene amaikana"
  69,50,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ilo lidzakhala lomvetsa chisoni kwa anthu osakhulupirira"
  69,51,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ichi ndi choonadi chokhachokha"
  69,52,"Motero lemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako, Wamkulu kulu"
  70,1,Wofunsa adafunsa za chilango chimene chichitike
  70,2,"Pa anthu onse osakhulupirira, chimene wina sangachiletse"
  70,3,"Kuchokera kwa Ambuye, Mwini njira zokwerera kumwamba"
  70,4,Angelo ndi Mzimu amakwera kupita kwa Iye mtsiku limodzi limene lingafanizidwe ndi zaka zikwi makumi asanu
  70,5,Kotero pirira kupilira kwabwino
  70,6,Ndithudi! Iwo amaona kuti ili patali
  70,7,Koma Ife tili kuliona lili pafupi
  70,8,Tsiku limene kumwamba kudzaoneka ngati mkuwa wachiphalaphala
  70,9,Ndipo mapiri adzakhala ngati ubweya wouluka
  70,10,Ndipo palibe bwenzi amene adzafunse za bwenzi lake
  70,11,Iwo azidzawaona iwo. Munthu wochita zoipa adzafunitsitsa kuti mwina akhoza kudzipulumutsa ku chilango cha tsikuli popereka ana ake
  70,12,Ndi mkazi wake ndi m’bale wake
  70,13,Ndi anansi ake amene adamusunga
  70,14,Ndipo zonse zimene zili padziko lapansi kuti mwina zikhoza kumupulumutsa
  70,15,Kosatheka! Ndithudi udzakhala moto wa lawilawi wa ku Gahena
  70,16,wotentha mutu wonse
  70,17,Udzaitana aliyense amene amakana choonadi
  70,18,Ndipo amangopanga chuma ndi kuchisunga
  70,19,Ndithudi Munthu adalengedwa kukhala wosapirira
  70,20,Amakhala modandaula ngati mavuto amupeza
  70,21,Ndipo amachita mwano ngati apeza zabwino
  70,22,"Kupatula okhawo amene amapemphera Al Ma’arij\t619 nthawi zonse"
  70,23,Iwo amene amapemphera mowirikiza
  70,24,Ndi iwo amene m’chuma chawo muli gawo limene amasiya padera
  70,25,Kuti apereke kwa anthu opempha ndi amene ali pa mavuto
  70,26,Ndi iwo amene amakhulupirira kuti kudzakhala tsiku lachiweruzo
  70,27,Ndi iwo amene amachita mantha ndi chilango cha Ambuye wawo
  70,28,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye ndi chosatetezeka
  70,29,Ndi iwo amene amadzisunga
  70,30,Kupatula akazi awo ndi akapolo awo chifukwa iwo sadzadzudzulidwa
  70,31,"Koma aliyense amene afuna kuposa awa, ndi wophwanya malamulo"
  70,32,Ndi iwo amene amasunga malonjezo ndi malamulo awo
  70,33,Ndi iwo amene amapereka umboni woona nthawi zonse
  70,34,Ndi iwo amene amalabadira mapemphero awo
  70,35,Awa ndiwo amene adzalemekezeka m’minda ya Paradiso
  70,36,Kodi chachitika ndi chiyani kwa anthu osakhulupirira kuti azibwera mwaliwiro kudza kwa iwe
  70,37,Kuchokera kumbali ya dzanja lamanja ndi mbali yakumanzere mu unyinji wawo
  70,38,Kodi aliyense wa iwo amayembekeza kukalowa m’munda wa chisangalalo
  70,39,Kosatheka! Ndithudi Ife tawalenga kuchokera ku chinthu chimene sachidziwa
  70,40,"Motero, Ine ndilumbira pa Ambuye wa malo onse a kum’mawa ndi kumadzulo kuti Ife tikhoza"
  70,41,Kuika anthu ena abwino m’malo mwawo ndipo palibe chinthu chimene chingatiletse kutero
  70,42,Motero asiye ayambe adzinyenga ndi chisangalalo mpaka pamene adzakumana ndi tsiku lawo limene adalonjezedwa
  70,43,Tsiku limene adzatuluka mwansanga m’manda mwawo ngati anthu a pa mpikisano umene amalandirirapo mphotho
  70,44,Atayang’ana maso awo pansi ndipo adzachititsidwa manyazi. Limeneli ndilo tsiku limene analonjezedwa
  71,1,"Ndithudi tidatumiza Nowa kwa anthu ake: “Chenjeza anthu ako chilango chowawa chisadafike pa iwo.”"
  71,2,"Iye adati: “oh inu anthu anga! Ndithudi ine, ndine Mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu.”"
  71,3,“Kuti muzipembedza Mulungu ndi kumuopa Iye ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  71,4,"“Iye adzakukhululukirani machimo anu ndi kukusungani bwino mpaka nthawi ya imfa yanu. Ndithudi nthawi ya Mulungu ikakwana, palibe wina aliyense amene angaibwezere m’mbuyo inu mukadadziwa.”"
  71,5,"Iye adati: “oh Ambuye! Ndithudi usana ndi usiku ndakhala ndiri kuwaitana anthu anga.”"
  71,6,“Koma kuitana kwanga kwangoonjezera kusamvera kwawo.”
  71,7,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, nthawi yonse imene ndiitana kuti Inu muwakhululukire, iwo amatenga zala zawo ndi kutseka m’makutu mwawo ndipo amatenga mikhanjo yawo ndi kufunditsa kumutu kwawo ndipo amapitirirabe kuchita zoipa monyada.”"
  71,8,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, ine ndidalalikira mokweza kwa iwo.”"
  71,9,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, ndidawalankhula pagulu ndi mwamseri.”"
  71,10,"Ndidawauza: “Funsani chikhululukiro cha Ambuye wanu. Ndithudi Iye amakhululukira nthawi zonse.”"
  71,11,"“Iye adzakutumizirani Nuh\t621 mvula yochuluka.”"
  71,12,"“Ndikukupatsani inu chuma, ana, minda ndi mitsinje.”"
  71,13,"Kodi mwatani, inu simuyembekeza mphotho"
  71,14,Pamene Iye adakulengani inu m’nthawi zosiyana siyana
  71,15,"Kodi inu simuona mmene Mulungu adalengera miyamba isanu ndi iwiri, wina pamwamba pa unzake"
  71,16,Ndipo anapanga mwezi ngati muuni ndi dzuwa ngati nyali
  71,17,Mulungu adakulengani inu kuchokera ku nthaka
  71,18,Ndipo ku nthaka komweko adzakubwezerani inu ndi kukudzutsaninso
  71,19,Ndipo Mulungu adalenga dziko kukhala lalikulu kwa inu
  71,20,Kuti muziyenda m’njira zambiri za zikuluzikulu
  71,21,"Nowa adati: “oh Ambuye! Anthu anga sali kundimvera ine koma mmalo mwake ali kutsatira amene sangawaonjezere chuma ndi ana koma mavuto.”"
  71,22,Ndipo iwo akonza chiwembu champhamvu
  71,23,"Ndipo ati: “Mwanjira ina iliyonse inu musaleke kupembedza milungu yanu. Musaleke kupembedza Wadd, Suwa, Yaghuth, Yauq kapena Nasr.”"
  71,24,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo asocheza anthu ambiri. Ndipo Inu musaonjeze china chili chonse kwa anthu ochita zoipa chifukwa apitirizabe kuchita zoipa.”"
  71,25,"Chifukwa cha machimo awo iwo anamizidwa ndipo adaponyedwa ku moto ndipo iwo sanapeze wina aliyense kuti awathandize, m’malo mwa Mulungu"
  71,26,"Ndipo Nowa adati: Ambuye wanga! Musasiye munthu aliyense padziko lapansi mwa anthu osakhulupirira"
  71,27,“Ngati Inu muwasiya iwo adzasocheretsa akapolo anu okhulupirira ndipo iwo adzabereka anthu ochita zoipa ndi osakhulupirira.”
  71,28,"“Ambuye wanga! Ndikhululukireni ine ndi makolo anga ndi iye amene alowa mnyumba yanga ngati wokhulupirira ndiponso okhulupirira onse amuna ndi akazi. Ndipo kwa anthu osakhulupilira, Inu musawaonjezere china koma chionongeko"
  72,1,"Nena: “Zavumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuti gulu la majini lidamvera chivumbulutso cha Mulungu ndipo lidati: Ndithudi ife tamva mawu odabwitsa.”"
  72,2,“Amene apereka dongosolo la kunjira yoyenera ndipo ife takhulupirira zonse zimene zinali kunenedwa ndipo ife sitidzalambira wina aliyense kupatula Ambuye wathu.”
  72,3,‘Ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wathu. Iye sadakwatire kapena kubereka ana
  72,4,‘Ndipo kuti anthu opusa amene ali pakati pathu akhala ali kumanenera Mulungu zinthu zonyasa kwambiri
  72,5,"‘Ndipo, ndithudi, ife timaganiza kuti kulibe munthu kapena majini amene angakanene chinthu chabodza chokhudza Mulungu"
  72,6,"‘Ndipo, ndithudi, padali anthu pakati pa mtundu wa anthu amene amapeza chitetezo kuchokera kwa anthu a mtundu wa majinn. Koma iwo adangoonjezera kuchita zoipa ndi kusakhulupilira"
  72,7,"‘Ndipo iwo adayamba kuganiza monga momwe inu mumaganizira, kuti Mulungu sadzadzutsa wina aliyense"
  72,8,‘Ndipo ife tidafuna kupita kuthambo la pamwamba zedi ndipo tidaona kuti linali lodzadzidwa ndi ogwira ntchito a mphamvu ndi nyenyezi za moto
  72,9,"‘Ndithudi ife tinali Al Jinn\t623 kukhala m’menemo kumvetsera koma amene azimvetsera tsopano, adzapeza malawi a moto uli kumudikira"
  72,10,‘Ife sitidziwa ngati akuwafunira mavuto anthu awo amene ali padziko lapansi kapena kuti Ambuye wawo ali ndi cholinga choti awatsogolere
  72,11,‘Alipo ena pakati pathu amene ndi angwiro pamene ena ndi ochimwa. Ife ndife magulu otsatira njira zosiyanasiyana
  72,12,‘Ndipo ife timaganiza kuti sitingathawe Mulungu padziko lapansi ndiponso sitingathawe pothamangitsidwa
  72,13,"‘Ndipo, ndithudi, pamene tidamva ulangizi wake, ife tidakhulupirira ndipo aliyense amene amakhulupirira mwa Ambuye wake sakhala ndi mantha otaya zake kapena kuponderezedwa"
  72,14,‘Ndipo pakati pathu pali ena amene amadzipereka kwathunthu kwa Mulungu ndi ena amene amachita zoipa. Iwo amene adzipereka kwa Mulungu amatsatira njira yoyenera.”
  72,15,Ndipo iwo amene amachita zoipa adzakhala nkhuni za ku Gahena
  72,16,"Ngati iwo akanakhulupirira ndi kutsatira njira yoyenera, Ife, ndithudi, tikadawapatsa mvula yambiri"
  72,17,Kuti tikhoza kuwayesa ndi izo. Ndi aliyense amene samvera chenjezo la Ambuye wake. Iye adzakonza kuti alandire chilango chowawa zedi
  72,18,Ndipo Mizikiti ndi ya Mulungu yekha. Motero musapembedze mulungu wina pambali pa Mulungu m’modzi yekha
  72,19,"Ndipo pamene kapolo wa Mulungu anaima kupempha kwa Iye, iwo adamuzungulira mu unyinji wawo mopanikizana"
  72,20,"Nena: “Ine ndimapempha kwa Ambuye wanga ndipo sindimufanizira Iye ndi wina aliyense.”"
  72,21,"Nena: “Ine ndilibe mphamvu yobweretsa pa inu chinthu choipa kapena kukubweretsani ku njira yoyenera.”"
  72,22,"Nena: “Palibe wina aliyense amene anganditeteze ine kwa Mulungu ndipo ine sindingapeze kothawira kwina kulikonse kupatula kwa Iye yekha.”"
  72,23,"“Udindo wanga ndi kukuuzani choonadi chimene ndalandira kuchokera kwa Mulungu ndi Uthenga wake, ndipo aliyense amene amanyoza Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake adzakhala ku moto wa ku Gahena nthawi zonse.”"
  72,24,"Mpaka pamene iwo ataona kuopsa kwa chilango chimene chidalonjezedwa kuti chidzafika pa iwo, pamenepo ndipo pamene adzadziwa mbali imene wopanda mphamvu ali ndipo kuti ndi ayani amene anali wochepa m’chiwerengero"
  72,25,"Nena: “Ine sindidziwa ngati chimene mwalonjezedwa chidzafika msanga kapena kuti Ambuye wangaadachiikapatali.”"
  72,26,Iyeyekhandiyeameneamadziwa zonse zobisika ndipo zinsinsi zake saululira wina aliyense ayi
  72,27,Kupatula kwa Atumwi ake amene Iye amawasankha yekha. Ndipo Iye amatumiza gulu la Atetezi amene amayenda patsogolo ndi pambuyo pawo
  72,28,Amawateteza mpaka pamene aona kuti iwo apereka uthenga wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo. Ndipo Iye amadziwa chili chonse chimene ali nacho ndipo Iye amasunga chiwerengero cha chinthu chili chonse
  73,1,Oh iwe amene wadzikulunga m’chovala
  73,2,Dzuka usiku onse kupatula kwanthawi kochepa
  73,3,Theka la usikuwo kapena kanthawi kocheperako
  73,4,Kapena kwa kanthawi kochulukirapo ndipo lakatula Korani modekha ndi modukizadukiza monga mmene umayenera kuchitikira
  73,5,"Ndithudi, Ife tidzakutumizira Mawu a mphamvu"
  73,6,"Ndithudi kuuka nthawi ya usiku ndi kovuta, ndipo mau amatchulidwa bwino"
  73,7,"Ndithudi, iwe masana umatangwanika kwambiri"
  73,8,Ndipo uzikumbukira dzina la Ambuye wako ndipo udzipereke kwathunthu kwa Iye
  73,9,Iye ndiye Ambuye wa kum’mawa ndi wa kumadzulo. Kulibe Mulungu wina koma Iye yekha. Mulandire Iye kuti akhale Mtetezi wako
  73,10,Pirira pa zonse zimene ali kunena ndipo siyana nawo mwaulemu
  73,11,Undisiyire Ine onse amene amakana choonadi nthawi zonse ndipo pirira ndi iwo pakanthawi kochepa
  73,12,"Ife, ndithudi, tili ndi unyolo ndipo tawasungira moto wosatha kuuzima"
  73,13,Ndi chakudya chotsamwitsa ndi chilango chowawa
  73,14,Patsiku limene dziko ndi mapiri zidzagwedezeka kwambiri ndipo mapiri adzakhala mulu wa mchenga wotaika umene umatuluka kupansi
  73,15,Ndithudi Ife tatumiza Mtumwi kukhala umboni wokutsutsani monga momwe tidatumizira Mtumwi kwa Farao
  73,16,Koma Farao sadamumvere Mtumwi ndipo Ife tidamulanga ndi chilango choopsa
  73,17,"Kodi ngati inu simukhulupirira, mudzalithawa bwanji tsiku limene lidzachititsa ana anu a ang’ono kukhala ndi imvi"
  73,18,Tsiku limene thambo la kumwamba lidzang’ambika pakati. Ndithudi lonjezo la Mulungu lidzakwaniritsidwa
  73,19,"Ndithudi ili ndi chenjezo chabe, motero musiyeni aliyense amene afuna kuti atsatire njira yoyenera yonka kwa Ambuye wake kuti aitsatire"
  73,20,"NdithudiAmbuye wako amadziwa kuti nthawi zina iwe umakhala tcheru mphindi ziwiri pakati pa mphindi zitatu za usiku, mwina theka la usiku ndipo nthawi zina mphindi imodzi pakati pa mphindi zitatu za usiku, monga momwe gulu lina la anthu amene ali nawe. Ndipo Mulungu ndiye amene amasiyanitsa usiku ndi usana. Iye amadziwa kuti siungathe kupemphera mphindi zonse ndipo wakuyang’ana mwachisoni. Kotero lakatula magawo ena a Korani amene angakhale apafupi kwa iwe. Iye amadziwa kuti pakati panu pali anthu odwala ndi ena amene ali kupita uku ndi uku padziko kufunafuna zokoma za Mulungu ndi ena amene ali kumenya nkhondo m’njira ya Mulungu. Motero lakatula, mawu a m’Korani, amene ungathe kulakatula, ndipo pitiriza kupemphera ndipo pereka msonkho wothandiza anthu osauka ndipo kongoza ngongole yabwino kwa Mulungu ndipo chabwino chilichonse chimene muli kutsogoza, mudzachipeza kwa Mulungu, chitasungidwa bwino ndipo mudzalandira mphotho ya mtengo wapatali kuchokera kwa Iye. Ndipo pempha chikhululukiro kwa Mulungu. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wa chisoni chosatha"
  74,1,ohiweamenewakutidwa
  74,2,Dzukandikuperekachenjezo
  74,3,Ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako
  74,4,Ndipo yeretsa zovala zako
  74,5,Ndipo pewa zonse za mafano
  74,6,Ndipo usapereke thandizo ndi cholinga chopezamo cholowa
  74,7,Ndipo khala wopirira chifukwa cha Ambuye wako
  74,8,Ndipo pamene lipenga lidzalira
  74,9,Ndithudi limeneli lidzakhala tsiku loopsa
  74,10,Tsiku lamavuto kwa anthu onse osakhulupirira
  74,11,Ndisiye ndekha kuthana ndi munthu amene ndidamulenga ndekha
  74,12,Ndipo ndidamupatsa chuma chosawerengeka
  74,13,Ndi ana okhala pambali pake
  74,14,Ndipo Ine ndidamuchitira zonse kuti zikhale zolongosoka ndi zapafupi
  74,15,Koma nthawi zonse amafuna kuti ndizimupatsabe zinthu zambiri
  74,16,Kosatheka! Ndithudi iye wakhala ali kuchitira mwano chivumbulutso chathu
  74,17,Ine ndidzamukhaulitsa pomupatsa chilango chowawa
  74,18,Ndithudi iye adaganiza ndipo adakonza chiwembu
  74,19,Ndipo ayenera kutembererewa chifukwa cha chiwembu chake
  74,20,Motero iye ayenera kutembereredwa chifukwa cha chiwembu chake
  74,21,Ndipo iye anayang’ana
  74,22,Ndipo iye adachita matsinya ndipo anaonetsa kuipidwa
  74,23,Kenaka adatembenukira kumbali modzikweza
  74,24,"Ndipo iye adati: “Ichi sichina koma matsenga a anthu a amakedzana!”"
  74,25,“Ichi sichina koma mawu a munthu chabe.”
  74,26,Ine ndidzamuponya iye ku Gahena
  74,27,Kodi chidzakudziwitsa kuti moto wa ku Gahena ndi chiani
  74,28,Iwo susunga kapena kusiya
  74,29,Umatentha matupi
  74,30,Umasamalidwandiangelokhumindiasanundianayi
  74,31,"Ife sitidasankhe wina aliyense koma angelo kuti aziyang’anira moto ndipo tinakhazikitsa chiwerengero chawo ngati mayesero kwa anthu osakhulupirira, kuti iwo onse amene alandira mawu a Mulungu akhulupirire ndi kuti anthu okhulupirira m’choonadi apitirize chikhulupiriro chawo; kuti iwo amene adalandira kale mawu a Mulungu ndiponso anthu onse okhulupirira moona asakhale ndi chikaiko china chilichonse; ndipo kuti onse amene m’mitima mwawo muli matenda pamodzi ndi anthu osakhulupirira anganene kuti: “Kodi Mulungu afuna kutanthauza chiyani pa chitsanzo chotere?” Mmenemo ndi mmene Mulungu amasokeretsera munthu aliyense amene Iye wamufuna ndi kutsogolera aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Palibe munthu amene amadziwa asirikali a Ambuye wako kupatula Iye mwini. Ichi si china chilichonse koma chikumbutso kwa anthu onse"
  74,32,"Iyayi, ndilumbira pali mwezi"
  74,33,Ndi pali usiku pamene uli n’kutha
  74,34,Ndi pali m’mbandakucha pamene uli n’kudza
  74,35,Ndithudi ili ndi limodzi la masoka akuluakulu
  74,36,Ndi chenjezo kwa anthu onse
  74,37,Kwa yense wa inu amene afuna kupitirirabe mtsogolo kapena afuna kutsalira m’mbuyo
  74,38,Munthu aliyense adzafunsidwa molingana ndi ntchito zake
  74,39,Kupatula iwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja
  74,40,"M’minda, iwo azidzafunsana wina ndi mnzake. Qiyamah"
  74,41,Za anthu ochimwa kuti
  74,42,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chakulowetsani inu ku moto
  74,43,"Iwo adzayankha nati: “Ife sitimapemphera.”"
  74,44,Ndiponso sitimadyetsa anthu a njala
  74,45,Ife timangotsutsa zinthu mwaumbuli
  74,46,Ndipo tidali kunena kuti kulibe tsiku lachiweruzo
  74,47,Mpaka pamene imfa idatipeza
  74,48,Motero palibe chidandaulo chochokera kwa wina aliyense chimene chidzamveka
  74,49,Kodindichifukwachiyaniiwoalikuthawachikumbutso ichi
  74,50,Monga abulu odzidzimutsidwa
  74,51,"omwe anali kuthawa Mlenje, Mkango kapena nyama ina yoopsya"
  74,52,Iai! Aliyense wa iwo afuna kuti apatsidwe masamba a Buku otambasula
  74,53,Ndikosatheka! Koma iwo alibe mantha ndi zimene zili nkudza
  74,54,Iyayi. Ndithudi ili ndi chenjezo
  74,55,Motero musiyeni amene afuna kuti awerenge ndi kulandira chenjezo
  74,56,"Ndipo iwo sadzalandira chenjezo pokha pokha ngati Mulungu afuna. Iye ndiye Ambuye wofunika kuti anthu onse azichita mantha ndi Iye, ndipo Iye ndi Ambuye wokhululukira"
  75,1,Ine ndilumbira pali tsiku lachiweruzo
  75,2,Ndipo ndilumbira pali munthu amene amadzidzudzula yekha
  75,3,Kodi munthu amaganiza kuti Ife sitidzalumikiza mafupa ake
  75,4,Inde Ife tikhoza kulumikiza mwaubwino nsonga za zala zake
  75,5,"Ngakhale tero, munthu amafuna kupitiliza kuchita zoipa"
  75,6,"Iye amafunsa: “Kodi zimenezi zidzachitika liti?”"
  75,7,Motero pamene maso adzathodwa
  75,8,Ndipo pamene mwezi udetsedwa
  75,9,Pamene dzuwa ndi mwezi zidzakumana
  75,10,"Patsikuli munthu adzafunsa kuti: “Kodi ndithawira kuti tsopano?”"
  75,11,Iai! Kulibe malo othawirako
  75,12,Ndi kwa Ambuye wako kokha kumene kudzakhala kothawira
  75,13,"Patsiku limeneli, munthu adzauzidwa zonse zimene adachita kuyambira poyamba mpaka pomaliza"
  75,14,Iai! Munthu adzadzichitira umboni wodzineneza yekha
  75,15,Ngakhale kuti iye azidzayesa kudzipulumutsa yekha
  75,16,Usagwedeze lilime lako zokhudza Korani ponena mofulumira
  75,17,Ndi udindo wathu kuisonkhanitsa ndi kukupatsa nzeru kuilakatula iyo
  75,18,"Ndipo pamene talakatula, tsatira mwandondomeko kalakatulidwe kake"
  75,19,Ndi udindo wathu kukufotokozera tanthauzo lake
  75,20,Iyayi!Komainumukondamoyowothamsanga
  75,21,Ndipo simufuna kulabadira za moyo umene uli nkudza
  75,22,"Nkhope zina, pa tsiku limeneli, zidzakhala zowala ndi chisangalalo"
  75,23,Zili kuyang’ana kwa Ambuye wawo
  75,24,"Ndipo nkhope zina, patsiku limeneli, zidzakhala zachisoni"
  75,25,Pozindikira kuti chilango chowawa chidzagwa pa iwo
  75,26,"Iyayi, pamene ufika mpaka pa khosi"
  75,27,"Ndipo kudzanenedwa kuti: “Kodi palibe woti angamuchize ndi kumupulumutsa ku imfa?”"
  75,28,Ndipo iye adzadziwa kuti awa ndi mathero a moyo wake
  75,29,Ndipo mwendo udzatembenuzika pa unzake
  75,30,Tsiku limeneli zonse zidzabwerera kwa Ambuye wako
  75,31,Iye sanali kuvomereza chilungamo kapena kupemphera
  75,32,Koma m’malo mwake adakana choonadi ndi kubwerera m’mbuyo
  75,33,Ndipo iye anapita kubanja lake monyada ali kudziyamikila yekha
  75,34,Tsoka kwa iwe. Ndiponso tsoka kwa iwe
  75,35,"Kachiwiri tsoka lili pafupi ndi iwe, tsopano tsoka lili pafupi"
  75,36,Kodi munthu amaganiza kuti tidzangomulekerera kuti azichita chilichonse chimene afuna
  75,37,Kodi iye sanali dontho la umuna limene lidatuluka
  75,38,Ndipo iye adakhala kam’bulu ka magazi. Ndipo Mulungu adamuumba ndipo adamukonza m’maonekedwe okongola
  75,39,"Ndipo adamulenga m’mitundu iwiri, mwamuna ndi mkazi"
  75,40,Kodi Iye alibe mphamvu yopereka moyo kwa anthu akufa
  76,1,Kodi sipadali nthawi imene munthu sanali kanthu kena kali konse kodziwika
  76,2,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu kuchokera ku madontho a umuna umene unasakanizidwa ndi ukazi ndi cholinga chomuyesa motero Ife tidamupanga iye kukhala wakumva ndi woona
  76,3,Ndithudi Ife tamulangiza njira yabwino kaya iye akhala wothokoza kapena wosathokoza
  76,4,Ndithudi tawakonzera anthu osakhulupirira unyolo ndi magoli ndi moto wa lawilawi
  76,5,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzamwa chakumwa chosakanizidwa ndi madzi ochokera pa kasupe wa ku Paradiso chotchedwa Kafur
  76,6,"Kasupe amene akapolo a Mulungu adzamwapo, amene amatumphutsa madzi ochuluka"
  76,7,Iwo amene amakwaniritsa malonjezo awo ndipo amakhala ndi mantha ndi tsiku limene zoipa zidzasefukira ponseponse
  76,8,"Ndipo amapereka chakudya chifukwa cha chikondi cha Mulungu, kwa anthu aumphawi, amasiye ndi kwa akaidi"
  76,9,Ife tili kukudyetsani chifukwa cha Mulungu basi. Ife sitifuna malipiro kapena mayamiko kuchokera kwa inu
  76,10,"Ndithudi ife tiopa tsiku loopsa ndi laululu limene lidzasanduliza nkhope kuoneka monyasa, limene lili nkudza kuchokera kwa Ambuye wathu"
  76,11,Motero Mulungu awapulumutsa iwo ku zoipa za tsiku limeneli ndi kuwapatsa nyali yokongola kuti akhale mosavutika ndi mwachisangalalo
  76,12,Ndipo mphotho yawo idzakhala munda wa Paradiso ndi zovala za silika chifukwa chopirira kwawo
  76,13,"Ali kukhala m’Paradiso, pamipando yawofowofo, iwo sadzamva kutentha kwa dzuwa kapena kuzizira kwambiri"
  76,14,Ndipo mithunzi idzakhala pafupi ndi iwo ndipo zipatso zidzalendewera mu matsanzi kuti asamavutike pothyola
  76,15,Ndipo pakati pawo padzaperekedwa zikho zozungulira za siliva ndi matambula a magalasi
  76,16,"Matambula oonetsa zinthu zomwe zili m’kati mwake, opangidwa kuchokera ku siliva. Iwo adzathiramo chakumwa molingana ndi chilakolako chawo"
  76,17,Ndipo iwo adzapatsidwa chakumwa kuchokera mu zikho zodzala ndi madzi osakaniza ndi Zanjabil
  76,18,Kasupe amene ali komweko wotchedwa Salsabil
  76,19,Ndipo adzazunguliridwa ndi ana owatumikira a misinkhu yofanana. Ndipo ngati iwe utawaona ukhoza kuganiza kuti ndi ndolo zomwazikamwazika
  76,20,"Ndipo pamene iwe uona kumeneko, udzaona madalitso ndi ufumu waukulu"
  76,21,Iwo adzavala nsalu zokongola za silika zooneka ngati msipu zopetedwa ndi golide. Iwo adzavala zibangiri za siliva ndipo Ambuye wawo adzawapatsa chakumwa chabwino
  76,22,Ndithudi iyi ndi mphotho yanu ndipo kupirira kwanu kwalandiridwa
  76,23,"Ndithudi ndife amene tavumbulutsa kwa iwe pang’ono pang’ono, Buku lolemekezeka la Korani"
  76,24,Motero pirira ndipo tsatira malamulo a Ambuye wako ndipo usamvere zonena za munthu wochimwa kapena wosakhulupirira amene ali pakati pawo
  76,25,Ndipo uzilemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako m’mawa ndi madzulo
  76,26,"Ndi m’gawo lina la usiku, uzimupembedza Iye ndipo uzimulemekeza Iye usiku wonse"
  76,27,"Ndithudi! Awa amakonda kwambiri moyo wa msanga msanga wa masiku ano, ndipo amaiwala tsiku limenelidzakhalalovuta"
  76,28,"Ndifeamenetidawalengandipo tinaika mphamvu m’ziwalo zawo. Koma ngati Ife titafuna, tikhoza kulenga anthu ena kuti alowe m’malo mwawo"
  76,29,"Ndithudi! Ili ndi chenjezo motero aliyense amene afuna, mulekeni kuti atsatire njira yoyenera yopita kwa Ambuye wake"
  76,30,Koma inu simudzatha kutero pokhapokha ndi chifuniro cha Mulungu. Ndithudi Mulungu ndiye Mwini kudziwa ndi Mwini nzeru
  76,31,"Iye adzaonetsa chisomo chake kwa aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Koma anthu ochimwa, Iye wawakonzera iwo chilango chowawa"
  77,1,Pali mphepo imene imatsatana pafupipafupi
  77,2,Pali mphepo ya mkuntho
  77,3,Pali mphepo imene imamwaza mitambo ndi mvula
  77,4,Pali mavesi amene amasiyanitsa chabwino
  77,5,Pali angelo amene amabweretsa chivumbulutso kwa Atumwi
  77,6,Kuthetsa kukangana kapena kuwachenjeza
  77,7,Ndithudi zonse zimene mwalonjezedwa zidzachitika
  77,8,Pamene nyenyezi zidetsedwa
  77,9,Ndi pamene thambo la kumwamba ling’ambika pakati
  77,10,Ndi pamene mapiri aphwanyika kukhala fumbi
  77,11,Ndi pamene Atumwi onse asonkhanitsidwa kukhala pamalo amodzi
  77,12,Kodi ndi tsiku liti limene izi zidzachitike
  77,13,Lidzakhala tsiku la chiweruzo
  77,14,Kodi ndi chiyani chidzakudziwitse zatsiku la chiweruzo
  77,15,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,16,Kodi Ife sitinaononge anthu a makedzana
  77,17,Kotero tidzaipanga mibadwo yotsatira kuti ione zomwezo
  77,18,Mmenemu ndi mmene timakhaulitsira anthu ochita zoipa
  77,19,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,20,Kodi sitidakulengeni inu kuchokera ku madzi onyozeka
  77,21,Amene tidasunga pamalo okhazikika
  77,22,Mpaka nthawi yake itakwana
  77,23,Motero Ife tinayesa ndipo Ife wodziwa kuyesa
  77,24,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,25,Kodi Ife sitinapange nthaka ngati malo okumaniranamo
  77,26,Amoyo ndi akufa
  77,27,"Ndipo tidalenga Al Mursalat\t635 mapiri atali pa dziko ndi kukupatsani madzi okoma kuti muzimwa"
  77,28,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,29,"(Zidzanenedwa kuti): “Pitani ku chilango chimene munkati sichidzabwera!”"
  77,30,"Pitani inu mu chithunzi, mu magulu atatu"
  77,31,Opanda mthunzi kapena pokhala pokutetezani ku malawi a moto
  77,32,Ndithudi! Umatulutsa malawi ake akulu akulu ngati nyumba zachifumu
  77,33,Ndipo ooneka ngati ngamira ya chikasu
  77,34,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,35,Patsiku limeneli iwo sadzatha kulankhula
  77,36,Ndipo sadzaloledwa kuti apereke chidandaulo
  77,37,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,38,Limeneli ndilo tsiku la chiweruzo. Ife takusonkhanitsani nonse pamodzi ndi anthu a makedzana
  77,39,"Tsopano ngati inu muli ndi chiwembu, chitani chiwembu chanu kwa Ine"
  77,40,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,41,Ndithudi anthu angwiro adzakhala mu mthunzi wozizira ndi pa akasupe
  77,42,Ndi zipatso zimene afuna kukhosi kwawo
  77,43,Idyani ndipo imwani mosangalala chifukwa cha zimene mudachita
  77,44,"Ndithudi, mmenemo ndi mmene timalipirira anthu angwiro"
  77,45,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,46,Idyani ndipo musangalale kwa kanthawi kochepa. Ndithudi inu ndinu oipa kwambiri
  77,47,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,48,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Weramani.” Iwo amakana kutero"
  77,49,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,50,Kodi ndi Uthenga uti woposa uwu umene adzaukhulupirire
  78,1,Kodi akufunsana nkhani zotani
  78,2,Ali kufunsana za nkhani ija yaikulu
  78,3,Nkhani imene akusiyana maganizo pakati pawo
  78,4,"Iyayi, iwo adzadziwa posachedwa"
  78,5,"Iyayi, iwo adzadziwa posachedwapa"
  78,6,Kodi Ife sitidapange dziko lapansi monga ngati kama
  78,7,Ndi mapiri ngati zikhomo
  78,8,Ndipo Ife tidakulengani inu awiri awiri
  78,9,Ndipo tidapanga tulo kukhala ngati mpumulo wanu
  78,10,Ndipo tidapanga usiku kukhala chophimba
  78,11,Ndipo tinapanga usana kukhala kopezera zofuna zanu
  78,12,Ndipo tidamanga mlengalenga miyamba isanu ndi iwiri
  78,13,Ndipo tidakhazikitsa mmenemo nyali yowala
  78,14,Ndipo tidatumiza mvula yambiri kuchokera ku mitambo ya mvula
  78,15,Kuti timeretse chakudya ndi mbewu
  78,16,Ndipo minda ya zomera zothinana
  78,17,Ndithudi tsiku la chiweruzo lidakhazikitsidwa kale
  78,18,Tsiku limene lipenga lidzalira ndipo inu mudzadza mu magulumagulu
  78,19,Ndipomumlengalengamudzatsegulidwa ndipo mudzakhala ngati makomo
  78,20,Ndipo mapiri onse adzayendetsedwa ndi kukhala ngati nthunzi yamadzi
  78,21,Ndithudi Gahena ili kuwayembekezera
  78,22,Mudzi wa anthu ophwanya malamulo
  78,23,Kumeneko ndiko kumene adzakhale mpaka kalekale
  78,24,Kumeneko sadzalawa chozizira kapena kumwa china chilichonse
  78,25,"Kupatula Al-Naba\t637 madzi owira ndi mafinya"
  78,26,Mphotho yoyeneradi
  78,27,"Chifukwa, ndithudi, iwo sanali kuopa chidzudzulo chathu"
  78,28,Ndipo iwo moyerekedwa anali kukana chivumbulutso chathu
  78,29,Ndipo Ife tidalemba m’Buku zonse zimene anali kuchita
  78,30,Motero inu lawani! Inu simudzalandira china chilichonse koma manzunzo ochuluka
  78,31,Ndithudi kwa anthu oopa Mulungu kudzakhala kupambana
  78,32,Minda ndi m’minda ya mphesa
  78,33,Ndi a namwali akulu akulu ofanana zaka
  78,34,Ndi chikho chodzadza
  78,35,Kumeneko iwo sadzamva mawu opanda pake kapena nkhani zabodza
  78,36,Imeneyi ndiyo mphotho yochokera kwa Ambuye wako ndipo ndi mphotho yokwanira
  78,37,"Ambuye wa Kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pawo, Mwini chisoni chosatha ndipo iwo sadzatha kulankhula naye"
  78,38,Patsiku limene Mzimu ndi angelo adzaima pa mizere ndipo palibe amene adzalankhula kupatula yekhayo amene adzalandira chilolezo cha Mwini chifundo chosatha ndipo adzanena chinthu chimene chili choona
  78,39,"Ndithudi tsiku limeneli ndi loona, motero iye amene afuna, mulekeni atsatire njira yobwerera kwa Ambuye wake"
  78,40,"Ndithudi takuchenjezani za chilango chowawa chimene chili nkudza posachedwa. Tsiku limene munthu adzayang’ana ntchito zimene manja ake adatsogoza, ndipo osakhulupirira adzati: “Kalanga ine, ndikanakhala dothi.”"
  79,1,Pali iwo amene amalanda mwankhanza
  79,2,Ndi pali iwo amene amachotsa mwaufulu
  79,3,Ndi pali iwo amene amauluka
  79,4,Ndi pali iwo amene amathamanga ngati ali pa liwiro loopsya
  79,5,Ndi pali angelo amene amakwaniritsa kuchita malamulo a Ambuye wawo
  79,6,Patsiku limene dziko ndi mapiri zidzagwedezeka kwambiri
  79,7,Ndi kulira kwa lipenga kawiri
  79,8,"Mitima, patsiku limeneli, idzafumuka ndi kuda nkhawa"
  79,9,Maso awo atagwetsa pansi
  79,10,"Iwo amanena kuti: “Kodi ife tidzabwerera monga momwe tinali poyamba?”"
  79,11,“Angakhale mafupa athu ataola?”
  79,12,"Iwo amati: “Kubwerera kotero ndi kopanda phindu.”"
  79,13,Koma udzakhala mfuwu umodzi okha
  79,14,"Pamene, taona, iwo adzadzipeza okha ali pamwamba pa nthaka ali ndi moyo"
  79,15,Kodiinumudaimvankhaniya Mose
  79,16,PameneAmbuye wake adamuitana mu dambo lodalitsika la Tuwa
  79,17,“Pita kwa Farao; Ndithudi iye waphwanya malamulo mopyola muyezo.”
  79,18,"“Ndipo ukamuuze kuti: Kodi ungadziyeretse wekha?”"
  79,19,“Ndi kuti ine ndikulondolere kwa Ambuye wako kuti uzimuopa Iye?”
  79,20,Kotero iye adamuonetsa chizindikiro cha chikulu
  79,21,Koma iye adachikana ndipo sanamvere
  79,22,Iye adapitirizabe kuchita zoipa
  79,23,Ndipo iye adaitana anthu ake onse ndipo anafuula mokweza
  79,24,"Nati: “Ine ndine Ambuye wanu wapamwamba mwamba.” Al-Naziat"
  79,25,Motero Mulungu adamugwetsera iye chilango chifukwa cha mau ake omaliza ndi oyamba
  79,26,Ndithudi mu izi muli phunziro lomveka kwa anthu oopa Mulungu
  79,27,Kodi inu ndinu ovuta kulenga kapena thambo la mlengalenga limene Mulungu adalilenga
  79,28,Iye analikweza m’mwamba ndi kulikonza bwino
  79,29,Usiku wake amaukuta ndi m’dima ndipo masana ake amatulutsa kuwala
  79,30,Ndipo pambuyo pake adalikulitsa dziko
  79,31,Ndipo anatulutsa madzi ndi msipu
  79,32,Ndipo adazika mapiri molimbika
  79,33,Chakudya cha phindu kwa inu ndi kwa zoweta zanu
  79,34,Koma pamene mavuto akulu akudza
  79,35,Tsiku limene munthu adzayamba kuganiza ntchito zake zonse
  79,36,Ndipo Gahena idzabweretsedwa pafupi kuti aliyense aione
  79,37,Ndipo kwa iye ophwanya malamulo
  79,38,Ndipo anasankha moyo wapadziko lino
  79,39,Ndithudi malo ake okhala ndi ku Gahena
  79,40,Koma kwa iwo amene amaopa kukaima pamaso pa Ambuye wake ndi machimo ndipo anali kudziletsa kuchita chifuniro chopanda pake
  79,41,Ndithudi adzakhala ku Paradiso
  79,42,Amakufunsa za nthawi imene chigumula chidzabwere
  79,43,Iwe siudziwa zoti unene china chili chonse
  79,44,Ndi Ambuye wako yekha amene amadziwa tsiku
  79,45,Iwe ndiwe mchenjezi chabe kwa iwo amene ali kuliopa tsikuli
  79,46,"Patsiku limene iwo adzachiona chigumula, kudzakhala ngati kuti iwo sanakhale padziko lapansi nthawi yaitali koma usiku umodzi kapena usana wokha"
  80,1,Iye anachita matsinya ndi kuyang’ana kumbali
  80,2,Chifukwa munthu wakhungu anadza kwa iye
  80,3,Ndipo iwe ungadziwe bwanji kuti mwina angadziyeretse
  80,4,Kapena iye adzalandira chenjezo ndipo chenjezo likanamupindulira kanthu kena
  80,5,Koma iye amene amadziyesa kuti sasowa kanthu
  80,6,Ameneyo ndiye amene uli naye ndi chidwi
  80,7,Kodi uli nazo chiani ngati iye sadziyeretsa
  80,8,Koma kwa iye amene amakuthamangira
  80,9,Ndipo iye amaopa
  80,10,Iwe siudamulabadire ayi
  80,11,Iyayi! Ndithudi chimenechi ndi chikumbutso
  80,12,Muloleni aliyense amene afuna kuti achilabadire
  80,13,Ichi chidalembedwa m’Buku la Mulungu lolemekezeka
  80,14,Loyeretsedwa ndi losungidwa bwino ndi loyera
  80,15,M’manja mwa Alembi
  80,16,Wolemekezeka ndipo womvera
  80,17,Atembereredwe munthu! Kodi ndi chiani chili kumuletsa kuthokoza
  80,18,Kodi Iye adamulenga kuchokera ku chiyani
  80,19,"Kuchokera ku dontho la umuna, Iye adamulenga ndipo adamukonza bwino"
  80,20,Ndipo Iye adamukonzera iye njira yapafupi
  80,21,Ndipo amamupha ndi kumusunga m’manda
  80,22,Ndithudi Iye adzamudzutsa monga momwe afunira
  80,23,"Iyayi, koma munthu sanachite zimene Iye adamulamulira"
  80,24,Mulekeni munthu kuti aganize za chakudya chake
  80,25,Kuti Ife timagwetsa mvula yambiri
  80,26,Ndipo timaphwanya nthaka
  80,27,"Ndipo Ife Al-Takwir\t641 timameretsa njere"
  80,28,Mphesa ndi Msipu
  80,29,"Mitengo ya mafuta, ndi mitengo ya tende"
  80,30,Ndi minda imene ili ndi mitengo yambiri
  80,31,Ndi mitengo ya zipatso ndi msipu
  80,32,Chakudya cha inu ndi ziweto zanu
  80,33,Koma pamene kulira kogonthetsa mkhutu kudzamveka
  80,34,Patsiku limene munthu adzakana m’bale wake
  80,35,Amai ake ndi bambo ake
  80,36,Mkazi wake ndi ana ake
  80,37,"Chifukwa aliyense patsiku limeneli, adzakhala otangwanika ndi mavuto ake"
  80,38,Patsiku limeneli padzakhala nkhope zambiri zowala
  80,39,Zosekerera ndi zachimwemwe chifukwa cha nkhani yabwino
  80,40,Ndipo pa tsikuli padzakhala nkhope zina zokutidwa ndi fumbi
  80,41,M’dima udzakuta iwo
  80,42,Awa adzakhala anthu osakhulupirira ndi ochita zoipa
  81,1,Pamene dzuwa lidzavundikiridwa
  81,2,Ndi pamene nyenyezi zidzagwa pansi
  81,3,Ndi pamene mapiri adzachotsedwa
  81,4,Ndi pamene ngamila zabele zizakhala zosasamalidwa
  81,5,Ndi nyama za m’tchire zidzasonkhanitsidwa pamodzi
  81,6,Ndi pamene nyanja zidzayatsidwa moto kapena zidzasefukira
  81,7,Ndi pamene mizimu idzakumanitsidwa ndi matupi awo
  81,8,"Ndi pamene mwana wa mkazi wa mng’ono, amene adaundilidwa wa moyo adzafunsidwa"
  81,9,Chifukwa chimene anamuphera
  81,10,Ndi pamene mabuku olembamo ntchito za munthu aliyense adzatulutsidwa
  81,11,Ndi pamene kumwamba kudzafafanizidwa ndi kuchotsedwa ku malo ake
  81,12,Ndi pamene Gahena idzatenthetsedwa kwambiri
  81,13,Ndi pamene Paradiso idzafikitsidwa pafupi
  81,14,Ndithudi munthu aliyense adzadziwa chimene adachita
  81,15,"Motero, ndithudi, Ine ndili kulumbira pali nyenyezi zimene zimalowa"
  81,16,Ndi pali maiko zimene zimayenda mofulumira ndi kudzibisa okha
  81,17,Ndi pali usiku pamene uchoka
  81,18,Ndipalim’mawapamenekulikucha
  81,19,Ndithudi awa ndi Mau a Mtumwi wolemekezeka
  81,20,"Mwini mphamvu amene amalemekezedwa ndi Ambuye, Mwini Mpando wa Chifumu"
  81,21,Amamveredwa ndi wokhulupirika
  81,22,Ndipo m’bale wanu uyu si wa misala ayi
  81,23,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iye adamuona iye mu mlengalenga"
  81,24,Iye sabisa zinthu zosaoneka
  81,25,Ndipo zimene alankhula sizochokera kwa Satana wotembereredwa
  81,26,Kodi inu muli kupita kuti
  81,27,Ndithudi ichi si china chilichonse ayi koma chikumbutso kwa anthu a mitundu yonse
  81,28,Kwa aliyense wa inu amene afuna kuyenda moongoka
  81,29,"Koma inu simungathe kutero pokhapokha ndi chifuniro cha Mulungu, Ambuye wa zolengedwe zonse"
  82,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambika
  82,2,Pamene nyenyezi zidzagwa ndi kubalalitsidwa
  82,3,Ndi pamene nyanja zikuluzikulu zidzaphulika
  82,4,Pamene manda adzatseguka
  82,5,Pamenepo Mzimu uliwonse udzadziwa chimene udatumiza ndi chimene udasiya m’mbuyo
  82,6,oh Iwe munthu! Kodi ndi chiyani chikukunamiza kuti usiye kutsatira malamulo a Ambuye wako Wolemekezeka
  82,7,Amene adakulenga iwe ndi kukukonza kuti uzioneka bwino monga mmene uonekeramu
  82,8,Ndi nkhope ina iliyonse imene idamukondweretsa anakulenga iwe
  82,9,Iyayi! Koma inu mukukana kuti kudzakhala tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,10,Koma pakati panu pali ena amene ali kukuyang’anirani
  82,11,Olemekezeka ndi odziwa kulemba
  82,12,Iwo amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  82,13,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzakhala mu mtendere
  82,14,"Ndipo, ndithudi, anthu onse oipa adzakhala ku Gahena"
  82,15,Imene iwo adzalowako ndi kulawa malawi ake patsiku lachiweruzo
  82,16,Iwo sadzatha kuthawa ayi
  82,17,Kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,18,Tinenanso kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,19,Ndi tsiku limene mzimu uliwonse sudzatha kuthandiza wina aliyense ndipo Mulungu yekha ndiye amene adzaweruza
  83,1,Tsoka kwa iwo onse amene amagulitsa malonda awo monyenga
  83,2,Iwo amene amati ena akamawayesera zinthu amafuna kuti zikwanire muyeso wake
  83,3,Koma pamene iwo ayesa kapena awayesera anthu ena amawanyenga
  83,4,Kodi iwo saganiza kuti adzaukitsidwa kwa akufa
  83,5,Patsiku lalikulu
  83,6,Tsiku limene anthu a mitundu yonse adzaima pamaso pa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  83,7,Iyayi! Ndithudi chiwerengero cha anthu onse oipa chili mu Sijjin
  83,8,Kodi udzadziwa bwanji Sijjin ndi chiyani
  83,9,Ili ndi Buku lolembedwa
  83,10,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  83,11,Iwo amene amakana kuti kuli tsiku lachiweruzo
  83,12,Palibe wina amene amalikana tsikuli kupatula munthu wogona m’machimo
  83,13,"Pamene chivumbulutso chathu chinenedwa kwa iye, iye amati: “Izi ndizo nthano za anthu akale.”"
  83,14,Iyayi! Koma m’mitima mwawo ndi mokutidwa ndi zintchito zimene amachita
  83,15,Iyayi! Ndithudi iwo sadzaloledwa kuona Ambuye wawo pa tsikuli
  83,16,Ndipo iwo adzalowa ndi kulawa moto ku Gahena
  83,17,"Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Chimenechi ndicho chilango chija munkachinena kuti sichidzakhalako.”"
  83,18,Iyayi! Ndithudi chiwerengero cha anthu olungama chimasungidwa mu Illiyyun
  83,19,Kodi mudzadziwa bwanji kuti Illiyin wapamwambayo ndi chiyani
  83,20,"Ndi Al Mutaffifin\t645 Buku lochita kulembedwa"
  83,21,Limene limaonedwa ndi iwo okhawo amene ali kufupi ndi zofuna za Mulungu
  83,22,Ndithudi anthu onse olungama adzakhala ku malo a mtendere
  83,23,Atakhala pa mipando ya wofowofo ndipo ali kuyang’ana uku ndi uku
  83,24,Ndipo udzaona chisangalalo pa nkhope zawo
  83,25,Iwo adzapatsidwa kuti amwe vinyo weniweni amene sanatsegulidwepo
  83,26,"Womaliza wake adzakhala ndi fungo labwino ndipo pachifukwa cha ichi, aleke onse amene afuna kulimbikira kuti alimbike"
  83,27,Wosakanizidwa ndi madzi a Tasnim
  83,28,Kasupe amene anthu odala adzakhala ali kumwa
  83,29,"Ndithudi! Anthu amene amachita zoipa, anali kuwaseka anthu amene anakhulupirira"
  83,30,Ndi kumacheulana iwo akamadutsa pakati pawo
  83,31,Ndipo iwo amati akabwerera kwa anthu awo amabwera ali kunyoza
  83,32,"Ndipo amati akawaona iwo amati: “Ndithudi awa ndiwo anthu osochera.”"
  83,33,Pamene iwo sadalamulidwe kuti akhale owayang’anira
  83,34,Koma pa tsikuli anthu okhulupirira adzaseka anthu osakhulupirira
  83,35,Ali pa mipando yawofowofo ndi kumayang’ana
  83,36,"Kodi anthu osakhulupirira, sanalipidwe mphotho yawo molingana ndi ntchito zawo"
  84,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambika
  84,2,Ndipo limva ndi kumvera Ambuye wake ndipo ling’ambikadi
  84,3,Pamene nthaka idzatambasulidwa
  84,4,Ndi kutulutsa zonse zimene zinakwiriridwa m’kati mwake ndi kukhala yopanda kanthu
  84,5,Ndipo limva ndi kumvera Ambuye wake ndipo ling’ambikadi
  84,6,oh iwe munthu! Ndithudi iwe uli kubwerera kupita kwa Ambuye wako ndi ntchito zako. Kubwerera kotsimikizidwa. Motero udzakumana nazo
  84,7,Koma Iye amene adzapatsidwa Buku lake m’dzanja lamanja
  84,8,Adzawerengedwa mosavuta
  84,9,Ndipo adzabwerera kwa anthu ake ndi chisangalalo
  84,10,Koma iye amene adzapatsidwa buku lake kumbuyo kwake
  84,11,Iye adzalira
  84,12,Ndipo akalowa ku moto walawi – lawi ku Gahena
  84,13,Ndithudi iye adali wansangala pakati pa anthu ake
  84,14,Ndithudi iye anali kuganiza kuti sadzabwerera kwa Mulungu
  84,15,Inde! Ndithudi Ambuye wake anali kuona zonse zimene iye ankachita
  84,16,Ine ndilumbira pali kufiira kwa kulowa kwa dzuwa
  84,17,Ndi pali usiku ndi zonse zimene umabweretsa mu mdima
  84,18,Ndi pali mwezi pamene ufika pa chimake penipeni
  84,19,"Ndipo inu, ndithudi, mudzayenda kupita kutsogolo, kuchoka apa ndi kufika apo"
  84,20,Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani choti iwo alibe chikhulupiriro
  84,21,Ndipo pamene Korani ili kuwerengedwa kwa iwo sagwa pansi. Al-Buruj
  84,22,Iyayi! Koma anthu osakhulupirira amalikana
  84,23,Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zinthu zonse zimene amasonkhanitsa
  84,24,Choncho auze iwo za chilango chowawa
  84,25,"Kupatula okhawo amene akhulupirira ndi kumachita ntchito zabwino, chifukwa iwo ali ndi malipiro opanda malire"
  85,1,Pali kumwamba kumene kuli nyenyezi zikulu zikulu
  85,2,Pali tsiku lolonjezedwa
  85,3,Pali tsiku la umboni ndi tsiku loperekedwa umboni
  85,4,wotembereredwa anali anthu amene anakumba ngalande
  85,5,Imene munali moto woyaka
  85,6,Pamene akhala moizungulira
  85,7,Ndipo iwo adachitira umboni pa zomwe amachitira anthu okhulupirira
  85,8,"Iwo analibe mlandu wina uliwonse ndi anthuwa kupatula kuti anali kukhulupirira mwa Mulungu mmodzi yekha, Mwini mphamvu zonse, Mwini kuyamikidwa"
  85,9,Mwini Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi! Ndipo Mulungu ndi mboni pa chilichonse
  85,10,"Ndithudi onse amene adazunza amuna okhulupirira, ndi akazi okhulupilira ndipo salapa machimo awo, adzalandira chilango chowawa cha moto woyaka wa ku Gahena"
  85,11,Ndithu onse amene akhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino adzakhala m’minda imene ili ndi mitsinje ya madzi oyenda. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu
  85,12,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako ndi chowawa
  85,13,Ndithudi Iye ndiye amene amayambitsa chilengedwe ndipo adzachibwereza patsiku louka kwa akufa
  85,14,Ndipo Iye ndi wokhululuka ndi wachikondi chodzadza
  85,15,"Mwini wake wa Mpando wachifumu, Wolemekezeka"
  85,16,Iye amachita chimene afuna
  85,17,Kodi iwe siudamve za asirikali
  85,18,A Farao ndi a Thamoud
  85,19,Iyayi! Koma anthu osakhulupirira amazikana
  85,20,Ndipo Mulungu amawazungulira onse
  85,21,Iyayi! Ili ndi Buku loyera la Korani
  85,22,Lolembedwa m’Buku lotetezedwa
  86,1,Pali kumwamba ndi pali Nyenyezi yowala
  86,2,Kodi chidzakudziwitsa kuti Nyenyezi yowala ndi chiani
  86,3,Ndi Nyenyezi yowala kothobwetsa maso
  86,4,Ndithudi moyo uliwonse uli ndi mtetezi wake
  86,5,Tamulekani munthu kuti aganize kuti adalengedwa kuchokera ku chiyani
  86,6,Iye adalengedwa kuchokera ku madzi otuluka
  86,7,Amene amatuluka kuchokera pakati pa pfupa la munsana ndi nthiti
  86,8,Ndithudi Iye ali ndi mphamvu zomudzutsa
  86,9,Pa tsiku limene zinthu zobisika zidzayesedwa
  86,10,Ndipo adzakhala wopanda mphamvu kapena womuthandiza
  86,11,Pali mtambo umene umapereka mvula kawiri kawiri
  86,12,Ndi pali dziko lapansi limene limang’ambika
  86,13,Ndithudi! Awa ndi mawu amene amasiyanitsa
  86,14,Si nthabwala ayi
  86,15,"Ndithudi iwo Al-A’la\t649 ali kukonza chiwembu"
  86,16,Ndipo Inenso ndili kukonza chiwembu
  86,17,Motero apatse nthawi anthu osakhulupirira. Ndipo chita nawo mwamtendere pa kanthawi kochepa
  87,1,Lemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako wapamwambamwamba
  87,2,Amene adalenga zonse ndi kuzikonza bwinobwino
  87,3,Amene adalamula tsogolo lawo ndi kuwatsogolera
  87,4,Amene amameretsa msipu
  87,5,Ndipo amausanduliza kukhala udzu ouma
  87,6,Tidzakuphunzitsa kulakatula chivumbulutso chathu ndipo sudzaiwala
  87,7,Kupatula chokhacho chimene Mulungu amafuna. Ndithudi Iye amadziwa chilichonse chooneka ndi chobisika
  87,8,"Ndipo Ife tidzakufupikitsira, m’njira yaifupi"
  87,9,Motero kumbutsa mwina chikumbutso chingawathandize
  87,10,Chikumbutso chidzalandiridwa ndi iye amene amaopa Mulungu
  87,11,Koma munthu wochimwa adzachisiya
  87,12,Amene adzaponyedwa mu ng’anjo yamoto ndi kulawa ululu wake
  87,13,Mmene iye sadzafa kapena kukhala ndi moyo
  87,14,Zoonadi iye amene adziyeretsa adzakhala wopambana
  87,15,Amene amakumbukira dzina la Ambuye wake ndipo amapemphera panthawi yake
  87,16,"Iyayi, koma inu mumasangalala ndi zinthu za m’moyo uno"
  87,17,Ndipo moyo umene uli nkudza ndi wabwino ndi wosatha
  87,18,Ndithudi! Zonsezi zidalembedwa mu Mabuku akale a Mulungu
  87,19,Mabuku a Abrahamu ndi Mose
  88,1,Kodi wamva za chinthu chachikulu chimene chili nkudza
  88,2,"Nkhope zina, patsiku limeneli, zidzachititsidwa manyazi"
  88,3,Pogwira ntchito zotopetsa
  88,4,Iwo adzalowa kumoto woyaka
  88,5,Iwo adzapatsidwa madzi oti amwe kuchokera kuchitsime cha moto
  88,6,Sadzakhala ndi chakudya china koma chiphe cha mtengo waminga
  88,7,Chimene sichidzawapatsa thanzi kapena kuthetsa njala
  88,8,"Nkhope zina, pa tsikuli, zidzakhala zosangalala"
  88,9,Adzakondwa chifukwa cha ntchito zawo
  88,10,Atakhala m’minda ya pamwamba
  88,11,Kumene iwo sadzamva zoononga kapena za bodza
  88,12,Mudzakhala kasupe wa madzi oyenda
  88,13,Ndi mipando yonyamuka ya wofowofo
  88,14,Ndi zikho zomwera zitaikidwa pambali pake
  88,15,Ndi makushoni yoikidwa m’mizere
  88,16,Ndi mikeka yoyalidwa bwino pansi pake
  88,17,Kodi iwo saona mmene ngamira zidalengedwera
  88,18,Ndi Kumwamba mmene kudakwezedwera
  88,19,Ndi mapiri mmene adalengedwera mokhazikika
  88,20,Ndi dziko mmene adalitambasulira
  88,21,"Motero akumbutse, chifukwa udindo wako ndi wowakumbutsa"
  88,22,Iwe sindiwe munthu wowakakamiza ayi
  88,23,"Kupatula iye Al Fajr\t651 amene abwerera m’mbuyo ndi kuyamba kusakhulupirira"
  88,24,Motero Mulungu adzamulanga chilango chachikulu
  88,25,Ndithudi onse adzabwerera kwa Ife
  88,26,"Ndipo, ndithudi, chiwerengero cha zochita zawo chidzakhala kwa Ife"
  89,1,Pali m’mbandakucha
  89,2,Ndi pali usiku khumi
  89,3,Pali chofanana ndi chosiyana
  89,4,Pali usiku pamene uli nkutha
  89,5,Ndithudi m’menemu muli umboni wokwanira kwa anthu a nzeru
  89,6,Kodi iwe siudaone mmene Ambuye wako adakhaulitsira anthu a Aad
  89,7,Amene anali atali atali ngati nsanamila zitali zitali
  89,8,wolingana nawo amene sanalengedwepo padziko
  89,9,"Ndi anthu a Thamoud, amene ankakumba nyumba zawo m’miyala ya m’dambo"
  89,10,"Ndi Farao, amene anali ndi zichiri"
  89,11,Amene anali kuphwanya malamulo paliponse m’dziko
  89,12,Ndipo adachulukitsa chisokonezo
  89,13,Motero Ambuye wako adabweretsa chilango chosiyana siyana chowawa pa iwo
  89,14,Ndithudi Ambuye wako amaona
  89,15,"Ndipo nthawi zonse munthu, pamene Ambuye wake amuyesa pomukweza ndi kumuonetsera chifundo chake, iye amati: “Ambuye wanga wandilemekeza ine.”"
  89,16,"Koma akamuyesa pomumana zinthu, iye amati: “Ambuye wanga ali kundizunza ine.”"
  89,17,Iyayi! Koma inu simuonetsa chifundo kwa ana a masiye
  89,18,Ndi kuuzana kuti mudzidyetsa anthu osauka
  89,19,Inu mumalanda chuma cha anthu opanda mphamvu chifukwa cha umbombo
  89,20,Ndipo mumakonda chuma ndi mitima yanu yonse
  89,21,Iyayi! Koma pamene dziko lidzasinjidwa kukhala ufa
  89,22,Ndipo Ambuye wanu adzadza pamodzi ndi angelo ali pa mizere
  89,23,"Ndipo Gahena idzabweretsedwa pafupi patsikuli. Ndipo patsikuli munthu adzakumbukira. Koma, kodi chikumbumtima chake chidzamuthandiza motani"
  89,24,"Iye adzanena kuti: “Kalanga ine! Ndikanakhala ndinali kuchita zabwino pamene ndinali ndi moyo.”"
  89,25,"Motero patsikuli, palibe wina amene adzalanga monga momwe Iye adzalangire"
  89,26,Ndipo palibe wina amene adzamanga monga ngati momwe Iye adzamangire
  89,27,oh! Iwe wokhutitsidwa
  89,28,"Bwerera kwa Ambuye wako mosangalala ndi Iye, ndi Iye mosangalala ndi iwe"
  89,29,Lowa m’gulu la akapolo anga wolemekezeka
  89,30,Ndipo lowa mu Paradiso yanga
  90,1,Ine ndili kulumbira pali Mzinda uwu
  90,2,Ndipo iwe uli ndi ufulu mu Mzinda uwu
  90,3,Ndi pali wobereka ndi chimene adabereka
  90,4,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu m’mavuto
  90,5,Kodi amaganiza kuti palibe wina aliyense amene ali ndi mphamvu pa iye
  90,6,"Iye amanena monyada kuti: “Ine Al-Shams\t653 ndaononga chuma chambiri.”"
  90,7,Kodi iye amaganiza kuti palibe wina amene ali kumuona
  90,8,Kodi Ife sitidamupatse maso awiri
  90,9,Ndi lirime ndi milomo iwiri
  90,10,Ndi kumulangiza iye njira ziwiri
  90,11,Koma sayerekeza kutsata njira yozyolika
  90,12,Kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za njira yozyolika
  90,13,Ndi kumasula kapolo
  90,14,Kapena kupereka chakudya nthawi ya njala
  90,15,Kwa wamasiye amene ndi wachinansi
  90,16,"Kapena munthu wosauka, wofuna chithandizo"
  90,17,"Ndipo iye anakhala mmodzi wa anthu amene akhulupirira, ndipo analangizana wina ndi mzake kupilira, kumva chisoni ndi kuonetsa chifundo"
  90,18,Iwo ndiwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja
  90,19,"Koma iwo amene anakana chivumbulutso chathu, adzaima ku dzanja lamanzere"
  90,20,Ndipo moto wa ku Gahena udzawakuta iwo
  91,1,Pali dzuwa ndi kuwala kwake
  91,2,Ndi pali mwezi umene umatuluka dzuwa litalowa
  91,3,Ndi masana pamene kumayera
  91,4,Ndi pali usiku umene umabisa
  91,5,Ndi pali Kumwamba ndi Iye amene adakulenga
  91,6,Ndi pali dziko lapansi ndi Iye amene analitambasula
  91,7,Ndi pali mzimu ndi Iye amene adaulenga
  91,8,Ndi kumupatsa iye nzeru zodziwa choipa ndi chabwino
  91,9,Ndithudi wopambana ndi amene amadziyeretsa
  91,10,Ndipo wolephera ndiye amene wadzidetsa
  91,11,Anthu a Thamoud adakana Mtumwi wawo poukiramoyerekedwa
  91,12,Pamenemunthuolakwakwambiri adayambitsa chipolowe
  91,13,"Ndipo Mthenga wa Mulungu anati kwa iwo: “Samalirani ngamira ya ikazi ya Mulungu ndi tsiku lake lomwa madzi!”"
  91,14,Iwo sadakhulupirire ayi ndipo ngamirayo adaipha. Motero Ambuye wawo adawaononga chifukwa cha machimo awo ndipo adafafaniza onse mosasankha
  91,15,Iye sadaope chotsatira chake
  92,1,Paliusikupamenemdimaumayamba
  92,2,Ndimasanapamene kumayera
  92,3,Ndi pali Iye amene adalenga chachimuna ndi chachikazi
  92,4,Ndithudi zochita zanu zonse zili ndi mapeto osiyana
  92,5,Akakhala iye amene amapereka chaulere ndipo amamuopa Mulungu
  92,6,Ndipo amakhulupirira pochita zinthu zabwino
  92,7,Ife tidzamusalazira njira yake ya ku chipulumutso
  92,8,Koma iye amene sapereka chaulere ndipo amaganiza kuti ndi woima payekha
  92,9,Sakhulupirira ndipo sachita ntchito zabwino
  92,10,Tidzamusalazira njira yake ya ku chionongeko
  92,11,Kodi chuma chake chidzamuthandiza chiani pamene iye azidzazunzika
  92,12,Ndithudi ndi udindo wathu kupereka chilangizo
  92,13,"Ndipo, ndithudi, zonse za m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndi za m’moyo uno ndi zathu"
  92,14,Motero ndakuchenjezani za moto wa lawilawi
  92,15,"Kulibe Al-Dhuha\t655 munthu amene akapsye nawo kupatula munthu wochita zoipa"
  92,16,Amene amakana choonadi ndipo safuna kumvera chenjezo
  92,17,"Koma anthu onse olungama, adzatalikirana nawo"
  92,18,Amene amapereka chaulere chake poonjezera kudziyeretsa
  92,19,Osati chifukwa chakuti afuna kupezako cholowa ayi
  92,20,"Kupatula ndi cholinga chopeza chisomo cha Ambuye wake, wapamwamba mwamba"
  92,21,Ndithudi iye adzasangalala
  93,1,Pali usana
  93,2,Ndi pali usiku pamene ulipo
  93,3,Ambuye wako sadakutaye iwe ndiponso sakudana nawe ayi
  93,4,"Ndipo, ndithudi, moyo umene uli nkudza ndi wabwino kwa iwe kuposa moyo uno"
  93,5,"Ndithudi Ambuye wako adzakupatsa, ndipo iwe chidzakukondweretsa"
  93,6,Kodi sadakupeze iwe uli wa masiye ndipo adakupatsa malo okhala
  93,7,Kodi sadakupeze uli wosochera ndipo Iye adakutsogolera
  93,8,Kodi sadakupeze iwe waumphawi ndipo adakulemeretsa
  93,9,Motero iwe usapondereze pansi mwana wa masiye
  93,10,Ndipo usapirikitse munthu wopempha
  93,11,Koma lengeza chisomo cha a Ambuye wako
  94,1,Kodi Ife sitidatsegule chifuwa chako
  94,2,Ndi kukuchotsa katundu wako wolemera
  94,3,Amene amalemetsa msana wako
  94,4,Ndipo tidakweza mbiri yako yabwino
  94,5,Ndithudi m’mavuto muli chithandizo
  94,6,Ndithudi m’mavuto muli chithandizo
  94,7,"Ndipo pamene wamaliza, pembedza Mulungu"
  94,8,Ndipo dzipereke kwathunthu kwa Ambuye wako
  95,1,Pali mtengo wa mkuyu ndi mtengo wa azitona
  95,2,Ndi pali phiri la Sinai
  95,3,Ndi pali Mzinda uwu wa mtendere
  95,4,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu m’chikombole chabwino
  95,5,Ndipo tinamutsitsa kukhala wapansi zedi
  95,6,"Kupatula amene amakhulupirira ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino, iwo adzalandira mphotho yosatha"
  95,7,"Kodi ndi chiyani, chimene chili kukupangitsani kukana tsiku la chiweruzo"
  95,8,Kodi Mulungu si woweruza wabwino kuposa oweruza onse
  96,1,Werenga! M’dzina la Ambuye wako amene analenga
  96,2,Yemwe adalenga munthu kuchokera ku kadontho kamagazi oundana
  96,3,werenga! Ndipo Ambuye wako ndiye wopereka mowoolowa manja
  96,4,Amene anaphunzitsa ndi cholembera
  96,5,Anaphunzitsa munthu chimene sanali kuchidziwa
  96,6,"Iyayi! Ndithudi, munthu amalakwa mopyola muyeso"
  96,7,Chifukwa amaganiza kuti iye ndi oima payekha
  96,8,Ndithudi! Nonse mudzabwerera kwa Ambuye wanu
  96,9,Kodi mwamuona munthu amene amaletsa
  96,10,Kapolo pamene akupemphera
  96,11,Kodi mwamuona ngati iye alikutsatira chilangizo chabwino
  96,12,Kapena kulamulira machitidwe abwino
  96,13,Ndiuze ngati iye akana choonadi ndipo salabadira
  96,14,Kodi iye sadziwa kuti Mulungu amaona zinthu zonse
  96,15,"Iyayi! Ngati iye sasiya, Ife tidzamududuluza pogwira tsitsi la pa mphumi pake"
  96,16,Mphumi yabodza ndi yochimwa
  96,17,Ndipo mulekeni iye aitane anzake oti amuthandize
  96,18,Ife tidzaitana osunga Gahena
  96,19,Iyayi! Usamumvere iye. Gunditsa mphumi yako pansi ndipo idza pafupi ndi Mulungu
  97,1,Ndithudi tinavumbulutsa ilo mu usiku wamphamvu
  97,2,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chingakuuzeni kuti mudziwe kuti usiku wamphamvu ndi otani
  97,3,Usiku wamphamvu ndi wabwino kuposa miyezi chikwi chimodzi
  97,4,"Mu usiku umenewu Angelo ndi Mzimu, ndi chilolezo cha Mulungu, amachoka kumwamba ndi kutsika pansi ndi malamulo ake onse"
  97,5,Mtendere mpaka m’mbandakucha
  98,1,"Iwo amene sakhulupirira a m’gulu la anthu a m’Buku ndi anthu opembedza mafano, sadzasiya kusakhulupilira mpaka pamene zizindikiro zooneka zitaperekedwa kwa iwo"
  98,2,Mtumwi wochokera kwa Mulungu amene ali kuwerenga kuchokera pa Masamba oyera
  98,3,Amene ali ndi malamulo angwiro ndi omveka bwino ochokera kwa Mulungu
  98,4,Ndipo anthu okhulupirira Buku sanayambe kugawikana pakati pawo mpaka pamene zizindikiro zooneka zidaperekedwa kwa iwo
  98,5,"Ndipo Al-Zalzala\t659 iwo sadalamulidwe koma kuti azipembedza Mulungu ndipo kuti asapembedze wina aliyense koma Iye yekha ndipo kuti adzipemphera pa nthawi yake ndi kupereka msonkho wothandiza anthu osauka. Ndipo chimenechi ndicho chipembedzo chabwino"
  98,6,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupirira amene ali pakati pa anthu a m’Buku, ndi anthu opembedza mafano, adzakhala ku moto wa ku Gahena. Iwo ndiwo oipa zedi pa zolengedwa zonse"
  98,7,Ndithudi iwo amene atsatira chikhulupiriro choonadi ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino ndiwo olemekezeka pa zolengedwa zonse
  98,8,"Mphotho yawo imene ili ndi Ambuye wawo ndi kuwaika m’minda imene imathiriridwa ndi madzi ya m’mitsinje pansi pake, kumene adzakhalako nthawi zonse. Mulungu ndi wosangalala ndi iwo ndipo nawonso ndi osangalala ndi Iye. M’menemo ndi m’mene munthu oopa Mulungu adzalandirire mphotho yake"
  99,1,Pamene dziko lidzagwedezeka ndi chivomerezi chomaliza
  99,2,Ndipo pamene nthaka idzatulutsa katundu amene ali m’kati mwake
  99,3,"Ndipo munthu adzafunsa: “Kodi yatani?”"
  99,4,Pa tsikuli nthaka idzaulula zonse
  99,5,Chifukwa Ambuye wako wayiuza kuti itero
  99,6,Pa tsikuli mtundu wa anthu udzadza m’magulu osiyana siyana kudzalangizidwa ntchito zawo
  99,7,"Motero aliyense amene amachita chabwino cholemera ngati njere ya mpiru, adzachiona"
  99,8,"Ndipo aliyense amene amachita choipa cholemera ngati njere ya mpiru, adzachiona"
  100,1,Palizothamangakwambirindikupumakwawokofulumira
  100,2,Ndi zimene zimaonetsa moto zikamathamanga
  100,3,Ndipo zimachita nkhondo m’mbandakucha
  100,4,Ndi kuonetsa fumbi
  100,5,Ndi kuphwanya pakati gulu la adani
  100,6,Ndithudi! Munthu sathokoza kwaAmbuye wake
  100,7,Ndipo mwini wake amachitira umboni zimenezi
  100,8,Ndithudi iye ali kukonda chuma kwambiri
  100,9,Kodi iye sadziwa kuti pamene zonse zili m’manda zidzatulutsidwa ndi kuonetsedwa poyera
  100,10,Ndizonsezimenezilim’mitimayaanthuzizidzaululidwa
  100,11,"Ndithudi, patsiku limeneli, Ambuye wako adzakhala ali kudziwa chilichonse"
  101,1,Tsiku louka kwa akufa
  101,2,Kodi tsiku louka kwa akufa ndi chiyani
  101,3,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chidzakuuze iwe kuti tsiku louka kwa akufa ndi chiani
  101,4,Ndi tsiku limene anthu adzakhala ngati dzombe louluka paliponse
  101,5,Ndi mapiri adzakhala ngati fumbefumbe za ubweya
  101,6,Ndipo iye amene muyeso wake wa ntchito zabwino udzakhala wolemera
  101,7,Adzakhala ndi moyo wa chimwemwe ndi chisangalalo
  101,8,Koma iye amene muyeso wake wa ntchito zabwino udzapezeka wopepuka
  101,9,Mudzi wake udzakhala dzenje lamoto
  101,10,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chidzakuuze zinthu zonsezi
  101,11,Ndi moto wa malawi osatha
  102,1,Mpikisano wosonkhanitsa chuma cha padziko wakutangwanikitsani inu
  102,2,Mpaka pamene inu mulowa m’manda
  102,3,Iyayi! Inu mudzadziwa
  102,4,"Kachiwiri, Iyayi! Inu mudzadziwa"
  102,5,Iyayi! Inu mukanadziwa kwenikweni
  102,6,Ndithudi inu mudzaona moto woyaka
  102,7,Kachiwiri inu mudzauona ndi maso anu
  102,8,Ndipo patsiku limeneli inu mudzafunsidwa za chisangalalo chimene munali kuchita
  103,1,Pali nthawi
  103,2,Ndithudi ! Munthu ndi otayika
  103,3,Kupatula okhawo amene amakhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino ndipo amalimbikitsana wina ndi mzake kuchita chilungamo ndi kukumbutsana kupirira
  104,1,Tsoka kwa aliyense amene amajeda ndi kuononga mbiri ya anzake
  104,2,Amene amasonkhanitsa chuma chake ndi kumachiwerenga
  104,3,Iye amaganiza kuti chuma chake chidzamuchititsa iye kukhala ndi moyo wamuyaya
  104,4,Iyayi! Ndithudi iye adzaponyedwa ku moto woononga
  104,5,Kodi chidzakuuza kuti moto woononga ndi chiyani
  104,6,Ndi moto wa Mulungu umene Mwini wake anauyatsa
  104,7,Umene umafuka m’mitima ya anthu
  104,8,Ndithudi udzawatsekereza mbali iliyonse
  104,9,M’sanamila zoima
  105,1,Kodi siudaone mmene Mulungu adachitira ndi eni ake a Njovu
  105,2,Kodi Iye sadasokoneze chiwembu chawo
  105,3,Ndipo anatumiza gulu la mbalame lolimbana nawo
  105,4,Zimene zinawalasa miyala ya moto
  105,5,Ndipo iwo adaoneka ngati msipu wodyedwa
  106,1,Pofuna kuteteza mtundu wa Quraish
  106,2,Kuti apitirire pa maulendo nthawi ya Chilimwe ndi m’nthawi ya Chisanu
  106,3,Motero auzeni kuti azipembedza Ambuye wa Nyumba ino
  106,4,Amene wawadyetsa m’masiku a njala ndi kuwachotsa mantha
  107,1,Kodi wamuona munthu amene amakana kuti kuli tsiku la chiweruzo
  107,2,Iye ndiye amene amazunza mwana wamasiye
  107,3,Ndipo sakakamiza anthu ena kuti azidyetsa anthu osauka
  107,4,Motero tsoka kwa iwo amene amapemphera
  107,5,Amene salabadira mapemphero awo
  107,6,Amene amachita zabwino pofuna kuti ena awaone
  107,7,Ndipo amakana kupereka chaulere
  108,1,Ndithudi takupatsa iwe Mtsinje wa Paradiso
  108,2,Motero pemphera chifukwa cha Ambuye wako ndipo upereke nsembe
  108,3,Ndithudi aliyense amene akukwiyitsa iwe adzakhala wopanda choyembekezera
  109,1,"Nena: oh! Inu anthu osakhulupirira"
  109,2,Ine sindipembedza chimene inu mupembedza
  109,3,Ndiponso inu simudzapembedza chimene ine ndipembedza
  109,4,Ndipo ine sindidzapembedza chimene inu muli kuchipembedza
  109,5,Ndipo inu simudzapembedza chimene ine ndimapembedza
  109,6,Kwa inu chipembedzo chanu ndipo kwa ine chipembedzo changa
  110,1,Pamene chithandizo cha Mulungu chidza ndi kupambana
  110,2,Ndipo uona anthu akulowa m’chipembedzo cha Mulungu mu unyinji wawo
  110,3,Motero lemekeza Ambuye wako ndipo upemphe chikhululukiro chake. Ndithudi Iye amavomera kulapa ndipo ndi wokhululukira
  111,1,"Aonongeke manja a Abu Lahab, ndipo nayenso aonongeke"
  111,2,Chuma chake ndi ana ake sizidzamuthandiza ai
  111,3,Iye adzalowa m’moto wa lawilawi
  111,4,Ndipo mkazi wake amene amanyamula nkhuni
  111,5,Mkhosi mwake muli chingwe chopota cha mlaza
  112,1,"Nena: Iye ndi Mulungu, mmodzi"
  112,2,"Mulungu, Mwini Mphamvu zonse"
  112,3,Iye sabereka ndipo Iye sadaberekedwe
  112,4,Ndipo palibe wina wofanana naye
  113,1,"Nena: “Ine ndifuna kuthawira kwa Ambuye wa M’mbandakucha"
  113,2,Kuchokera ku zinthu zonyansa zimene walenga
  113,3,Ndi kuchokera ku zonyansa za nthawi ya usiku pamene mdima ufika
  113,4,Ndi kuchokera ku zonyansa za anthu a matsenga pamene auzila pfundo
  113,5,“Ndi ku zonyansa za munthu wa dumbo pamene achita nsanje.”
  114,1,"Nena: “Ine ndifuna kuthawira kwa Ambuye wa anthu"
  114,2,Mfumu ya anthu
  114,3,Mulungu wa anthu
  114,4,Kuchokera ku zonyansa za kazitape amene amachoka akatha
  114,5,Amene amanong’oneza m’mitima mwa anthu
  114,6,Ya majini ndi anthu.”